        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post Birch Landing 500 Maxham Rd Austell, GA 30168 Reach out via phone: show contact info Apartment Information: 2 Bedroom | 2.5 Bath Apartment Size: 1350 sq ft Monthly Price: $1479 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Lease Terms: 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month Apartment Includes: ŌŚŠ Air Conditioning/Heating ŌŚŠ Balcony/Patio in Select Units ŌŚŠ Cable Ready ŌŚŠ Carpet ŌŚŠ Dining Room ŌŚŠ Extra Storage ŌŚŠ Garden Tub ŌŚŠ Handrails ŌŚŠ Hardwood Floors ŌŚŠ High Speed Internet Access ŌŚŠ Kitchen ŌŚŠ Office ŌŚŠ Range ŌŚŠ Refrigerator/Freezer ŌŚŠ Scenic View ŌŚŠ Trash Compactor ŌŚŠ Tub/Shower ŌŚŠ Vaulted Ceiling ŌŚŠ Walk-In Closets ŌŚŠ Washer/Dryer Hookup in Select Units Property Description: Whether you're preparing a meal in your beautiful gourmet kitchen, enjoying the fresh air out on your own private patio, or unwinding after a long day beside your cozy wood burning stone fireplace, you'll fall in love with where you live over and over again. With spacious, thoughtfully planned layouts and convenient extra features like full size washers and dryer connections, Garden Tubs, extra storage and an abundance of natural light, our apartments for rent in Austell, GA really do have it all. Come home to Birch Landing and discover what real living is all about. Property Amenities: ŌŚŠ BBQ/Picnic Area ŌŚŠ Business Center ŌŚŠ Clubhouse ŌŚŠ Conference Room ŌŚŠ Controlled Access Gate ŌŚŠ Indoor Pool & Jacuzzi ŌŚŠ Laundry Facilities ŌŚŠ Maintenance on site ŌŚŠ Online Services ŌŚŠ Parking ŌŚŠ Planned Social Activities ŌŚŠ Playground ŌŚŠ Preferred Employer Discounts Available ŌŚŠ Property Manager on Site ŌŚŠ Public Transportation ŌŚŠ Smoke Free ŌŚŠ Sparkling Outdoor Pool ŌŚŠ Storage Space ŌŚŠ Tennis Courts ŌŚŠ Townhomes Available Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/BirchLandingApartments/ Website: www.apts-rental.com?n=birch_landing&rp=qYZ1UT8Y6Yae&t=wb Online Application: www.apts-rental.com?n=birch_landing&rp=qYZ1UT8Y6Yae&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.apts-rental.com?n=birch_landing&rp=qYZ1UT8Y6Yae&t=sch Reach out via phone: show contact info Mon - Fri: 9:00 AM - 5:00 PM Sat: 10:00 AM - 5:00 PM Sun: 1:00 PM - 4:30 PM Pet Ownership Policy: We welcome 2 pets per apartment home. There is a maximum of 50lbs combined weight of 2 pets. There is a one-time pet fee of $325. Please call for complete pet policy information. $20 Pet Monthly Rent. All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY A5EBCC31578F4B",
