s a maximum of 50lbs combined weight of 2 pets. There is a one-time pet fee of $325. Please call for complete pet policy information. $20 Pet Monthly Rent. Leasing Options: 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/BirchLandingApartments/ Website: www.lease-apts.com?n=birch_landing&rp=2yXj1qqCVQzv&t=wb Online Application: www.lease-apts.com?n=birch_landing&rp=2yXj1qqCVQzv&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.lease-apts.com?n=birch_landing&rp=2yXj1qqCVQzv&t=sch All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 24BEDFD442184C",
