        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Polo Club Apartments - A place to call home! Bed: 3 / Bath: 2 Sq. Footage: 1300 sq ft Monthly Price: $1495 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Terms: 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month Call: show contact info The living spaces at Polo Club Apartments are thoughtfully designed for comfort and convenience in mind, and are stylishly appointed with the kind of premium materials and finishes you won't find in any other rental apartments in Stone Mountain, GA. Our Apartment Homes Feature: ŌØ¢ Breakfast Bar ŌØ¢ Cable Ready ŌØ¢ Carpet ŌØ¢ Dining Room ŌØ¢ Dishwasher ŌØ¢ Disposal ŌØ¢ Extra Storage ŌØ¢ Range ŌØ¢ Tub/Shower ŌØ¢ Vinyl Flooring ŌØ¢ Air Conditioning and Gas Heating ŌØ¢ Brushed Nickel Lighting Package ŌØ¢ Cozy Fireplaces ŌØ¢ Huge Floorplans up to 1300 sq. ft. ŌØ¢ Newly Updated Apartments ŌØ¢ Patio or Balcony ŌØ¢ Roommate Floor Plans ŌØ¢ Walk-In Closets ŌØ¢ Washer & Dryer Connections Our Residents Enjoy: ŌØ¢ Business Center ŌØ¢ Clubhouse ŌØ¢ Community Events ŌØ¢ On Marta bus-line ŌØ¢ Pet Care ŌØ¢ Picnic Area ŌØ¢ Playground ŌØ¢ Tennis Court ŌØ¢ Cardio & Fitness Center ŌØ¢ Clothes Care Center ŌØ¢ Electronic Rent Payment ŌØ¢ Minutes to Stone Mountain park ŌØ¢ On-Site Management ŌØ¢ Package Receiving ŌØ¢ Resort Style Swimming Pool ŌØ¢ Shopping, Dining, and Entertainment Nearby Call: show contact info 100 Ashley Creek Cir Stone Mountain, GA 30083 Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/poloclubapartments Website: www.apts-rental.com?n=polo_club&rp=jdPjjz9JfUT6&t=wb Online Application: www.apts-rental.com?n=polo_club&rp=jdPjjz9JfUT6&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.apts-rental.com?n=polo_club&rp=jdPjjz9JfUT6&t=sch Mon - Fri: 8:30 AM - 5:30 PM Sat: 10:00 AM - 5:00 PM Sun: 1:00 PM - 5:00 PM Pets: A maximum of 2 pets per unit shall be accepted. The pet fee is $350 Non-Refundable per pet. $30 monthly pet rent. A pet addendum must be completed, and pet fees must be paid prior to moving in. If there is more than one pet per unit, the combined weight of the 2 pets cannot exceed 50 lbs. For more information, please call our leasing office. Equal Housing Opportunity. All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY A2B702820CD84E1",
