        "ver": "Townhouse",
        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post Beautifully Updated 2 Bed / 2.5 Bath Townhome in Highgate at Sandy Springs 6900 Roswell Rd, F4, Sandy Springs, GA 30328 2600.00 / Month 2 BEDROOMS | 2.5 BATHROOMS Interested? Fill out this form : https://renter.turbotenant.com/general-prescreener/T3duZXI6NjY4MjU3?property=1245429&source=cl Have questions? Contact the Landlord : https://rental.turbotenant.com/p/6900-roswell-rd-sandy-springs-ga-unit-f4/cc66832c-de78-4321-abca-5e61277d3c41?source=craigslist Property Description: Available September 1, 2026 (Potentially available sooner for qualified applicants.) Welcome home to this beautifully updated 1,324 sq. ft. townhome in the gated Highgate at Sandy Springs community. Featuring a spacious roommate-style floor plan, modern finishes, and resort-style amenities, this home is ideal for professionals, roommates, graduate students, or anyone looking for low-maintenance living in one of Metro Atlanta's most convenient locations. Prime Location 5 min to I-285 & GA-400 10 min to Perimeter Center 12 min to Downtown Roswell 15 min to Midtown Atlanta 15ŌĆō20 min to The Battery/Truist Park Minutes from Buckhead, Northside Hospital, Children's Healthcare of Atlanta, shopping, restaurants, and parks. Home Features ŌĆó 2 oversized bedrooms with private en-suite bathrooms ŌĆó 2.5 updated bathrooms ŌĆó Granite countertops ŌĆó Large walk-in closets + extra storage ŌĆó Washer & dryer included ŌĆó Dishwasher & garbage disposal ŌĆó Central A/C & forced-air heat ŌĆó 2 reserved parking spaces + guest parking Community Amenities Gated community ŌĆó Pool ŌĆó Fitness center ŌĆó Dog park ŌĆó Beautifully maintained grounds Rent Includes Water, sewer, trash, HOA dues, exterior maintenance, and landscapingŌĆösaving you time and monthly expenses. Tenant Responsible For Electric, gas, and internet. Lease Details 12- or 24-month lease options available. Security deposit equal to one month's rent. First month's rent and Security Deposit due before move-in. Pets considered with owner and HOA approval ($350 non-refundable pet fee per approved pet). Credit, background, rental history, and income verification required. This move-in-ready townhome combines comfort, convenience, and an unbeatable Sandy Springs location. Schedule your private showing today! Property Type : Townhouse Pets : Cats, Small Dogs, Large Dogs Allowed Smoking : OUTSIDE_ONLY Lease Term : 2600.00 / Month 2600.00 Deposit Lease Length: Contact For Details Available: 09/01/2026 Occupancy Limit: 4 People Utilities Included : Sewage Water Garbage Recycling Appliances : Dishwasher Garbage Disposal Refrigerator Dryer Microwave Washer Freezer Range Oven Amenities : Cable Ready Fitness Center Swimming Pool Near Parks Secure Building Bicycle Parking Security Cameras Wired For Internet Balcony Or Deck Heating & Cooling : Forced Air Central Interested? Fill out this form : https://renter.turbotenant.com/general-prescreener/T3duZXI6NjY4MjU3?property=1245429&source=cl Have questions? Contact the Landlord : https://rental.turbotenant.com/p/6900-roswell-rd-sandy-springs-ga-unit-f4/cc66832c-de78-4321-abca-5e61277d3c41?source=craigslist",
