        "geocode_query": "925 Whitlock Ave.",
        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post RENTAL INFO Monthly Price: $1230 - $1550 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Magnolia at Whitlock: 925 Whitlock Ave. NW Marietta, GA 30064 Apartment for Rent: 2-BR 2-BA | Square Feet: 1150 sq ft | Lease Length: 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month, 13-Month, 14-Month Call us: show contact info PROPERTY AMENITIES ŌØ¢ 24-7 Emergency Maintenance ŌØ¢ Brand New Resident Clubroom ŌØ¢ Business Center/WiFi Bar ŌØ¢ Free Weights ŌØ¢ Outdoor Grilling &amp Picnic Area ŌØ¢ Pet Friendly ŌØ¢ Pet Wash ŌØ¢ Smart Cardio Equipment ŌØ¢ State-of-the-Art Fitness Center ŌØ¢ Valet Trash Service ŌØ¢ 15 Minutes to Lockheed and Dobbins Air Force Base ŌØ¢ Brand New Fully-Renovated Clubhouse ŌØ¢ Minutes to Historic Marietta Square ŌØ¢ Onsite Professional Management Team ŌØ¢ Resort-Style Swimming Pool with Sun Soaked Seating APARTMENT AMENITIES ŌØ¢ Air Conditioner ŌØ¢ Ceiling Fan in select units ŌØ¢ Oversized Living Areas ŌØ¢ Plush Carpeting ŌØ¢ Pool View ŌØ¢ Top Floor ŌØ¢ Valet trash ŌØ¢ W/D Hookup ŌØ¢ Wall-to-wall carpet ŌØ¢ Washer/Dryer* ŌØ¢ Ample Closet Space ŌØ¢ Central heat and air conditioning ŌØ¢ Extra Storage Available ŌØ¢ Fully Equipped Kitchen ŌØ¢ Spacious balcony or enclosed private patio ADDITIONAL INFO Description: Magnolia at Whitlock offers spacious, move-in-ready homes with updated interiors and modern finishes. Each apartment is designed for comfort, with features that make settling in easy from day one. It's a fresh start in a quiet, well-connected Marietta neighborhood. Pet Policy: Pet Guidelines Allowed pets include dogs, cats, fish, birds, and hamsters Pet fees or pet rent apply to dogs and cats only Up to two pets per home Exotic pets or livestock are not permitted Fish tanks may not exceed 24 gallons Breed Restrictions For more information on restrictions or pet-related fees, contact our leasing team. We're happy to help you and your pets find the purr-fect fit! Website: www.rentalsapts.com?n=magnolia_at_whitlock&rp=w3b6Xkt83nfD&t=wb Online Application: www.rentalsapts.com?n=magnolia_at_whitlock&rp=w3b6Xkt83nfD&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.rentalsapts.com?n=magnolia_at_whitlock&rp=w3b6Xkt83nfD&t=sch Call us: show contact info Administrative Fee $100 All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 1KSN0LBAX47914Z",
