Policy: Brookside Park Apartments is a pet friendly community that welcome two pets per apartment home. The pet fee is $325 non-refundable per pet. There is a $20 monthly pet rent. A pet addendum must be completed, and pet fees must be paid prior to moving in. If there is more than one pet per unit, the combined weight of the 2 pets cannot exceed 50 lbs. Breed restrictions may apply. Lease-Length: 6-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month Take 75 South to Langford Parkway (Hwy 166 West) to 1st exit (Metropolitan Pkwy). At light, take right. Turn left at next light, which is Metropolitan Pkwy. Turn right on St. Johns Ave. Brookside Park is on the left. All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 0A21EB13FF9940",
