        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post Come home to a great community - Spring Lake Apartments! Address: 7000 Southlake Pkwy Morrow, GA 30260 Call us at show contact info Beds: 1 / Baths: 1 / Size: 842 sq ft Monthly Price: $1261 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Spring Lake Apartments, where location and convenience are combined with luxuries to create a unique living experience in Morrow, Georgia. Professionally managed by Ventron Management, our 1 and 2 bedroom apartments offer exceptional features. Residents enjoy our peaceful lake views, full size washers and dryer connections, and spacious floor plans. Spring Lake Apartments offers amenities that make living here both comfortable and convenient. Work out in our fitness center, relax by the pool or enjoy an afternoon by our beautiful community lake. We offer wi-fi in our community clubhouse, picnic areas by the lake, and a luxury swimming pool. We invite you to call us for more information or come by Spring Lake Apartments and see why our residents love to call us home! We look forward to showing you around our community. Deposit: $400 Length of Lease: 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month Property Features: ŌŚÅ Clothes Care Center ŌŚÅ Clubhouse w/WIFI ŌŚÅ Clubroom ŌŚÅ Courtyard ŌŚÅ Fitness Center ŌŚÅ Package Receiving ŌŚÅ Pet Care ŌŚÅ Waterfront ŌŚÅ Community Playground ŌŚÅ Flexible Lease Terms ŌŚÅ Maintenance on site ŌŚÅ Picnic Areas & Gazebos ŌŚÅ Picnic Pavilion with Grills ŌŚÅ Relaxing Community Lake ŌŚÅ Relaxing Community Lake & Pavilion ŌŚÅ Resort Inspired Pool Apartment Amenities: ŌŚÅ Balcony/Patio ŌŚÅ Dishwasher ŌŚÅ Disposal ŌŚÅ Fireplace ŌŚÅ Linen Closets ŌŚÅ Oven/Range ŌŚÅ Spacious Sunrooms ŌŚÅ Storage Units ŌŚÅ W/D Connections ŌŚÅ Walk-In Closets ŌŚÅ Air Conditioning and Heating ŌŚÅ Brushed Nickel Hardware ŌŚÅ Brushed Nickel Lighting ŌŚÅ Ceiling Fans with Lighting ŌŚÅ Fully Equipped Kitchens ŌŚÅ Granite Inspired Countertops ŌŚÅ High Speed Internet Access ŌŚÅ Refrigerator and Freezer/Ice Maker ŌŚÅ Renovated Suites Available ŌŚÅ Separate Dining Areas Pets: Spring Lake Apartments is a pet-friendly community that welcomes two pets per apartment home. The pet fee is $300 non-refundable per pet. Monthly Pet Rent is $25. A pet addendum must be completed, and pet fees must be paid prior to moving in. If there is more than one pet per unit, the combined weight of the 2 pets cannot exceed 50 lbs. Breed restrictions may apply. Business Hours: Mon - Fri: 8:30 AM - 5:30 PM Sat: 10:00 AM - 5:00 PM Ready to Lease? Call us at show contact info Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/springlakeatl Website: www.apts-rental.com?n=spring_lake&rp=5XY3sADocqL5&t=wb Online Application: www.apts-rental.com?n=spring_lake&rp=5XY3sADocqL5&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.apts-rental.com?n=spring_lake&rp=5XY3sADocqL5&t=sch All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 2D88E72A5CD94D0",
