        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post Come home to a great community - IMT Alpharetta! Address: 3500 North Point Parkway Alpharetta, GA 30005 Contact us for more information! show contact info Beds: 3 / Baths: 2 / Size: 1275 sq ft Monthly Price: $2440 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. **Walk-ins welcome & choose from 3 tour options.** IMT Alpharetta is comprised of one-, two- and three-bedroom apartment homes located in the beautiful suburb of Alpharetta, GA. Each home includes an array of interior amenities from fully equipped gourmet kitchens to in-home washer/dryers to a private patio, balcony or sunroom, perfect for relaxation. Community amenities include a lighted tennis court, a resort-style pool, a playground and more. IMT Alpharetta is located within the blue award-winning Creekview Elementary, Webb Bridge Middle & Alpharetta high school districts and has close proximity to Avalon Shopping District and North Point Mall. With close proximity to MARTA, IMT Alpharetta gives residents an easy commute and all the best that the greater Alpharetta area has to offer. Lease terms are 3-12, 24. Come home to IMT Alpharetta. Take a Virtual Tour of Our Property Today! https://liveimt.com/imtAlpharettaYoutubeTour Price shown is Total Monthly Price including monthly mandatory fees* Monthly Mandatory Fees: - Package Locker: $5/month - Credit Reporting: $5/month - Water Charges: Varies - Sewer Charges: Varies - Pest: $4.50/month - Service Fee: $3.99/month - Trash Service: $10/month Deposit: Call Length of Lease: 3-Month, 4-Month, 5-Month, 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month Property Features: Ō£ō Car Care Center Ō£ō Playground Ō£ō Pool Ō£ō Access to Big Creek Greenway Walking Trails Ō£ō Close Proximity to Avalon Shopping District & North Point Mall Ō£ō Emergency Maintenance Service Ō£ō Lighted Tennis Court Ō£ō MARTA Public Transportation Access Ō£ō Online & On-Site Kiosk Access Ō£ō Resort-Style Pool with Lap Lanes Ō£ō Within Blue Award Winning Webb Bridge Middle & Alpharetta High School Districts Apartment Amenities: Ō£ō Black or Stainless Steel Appliances in Classic Hom Ō£ō Ceiling Fan Ō£ō Eight-Foot Ceilings Ō£ō In-Home Washer/Dryer Ō£ō Stainless Steel Appliances in Upgraded Homes Ō£ō Sunroom in Select Homes Ō£ō Walk-In Closets Ō£ō Wood-Burning Fireplaces in Select Homes Ō£ō Wood-Style Blinds Ō£ō Wood-Style Flooring in Living Areas in Upgraded Homes Pets: Pets allowed! Two pet maximum. Pet fee (non-refundable) is $300 per pet. Pet rent is $25 per month per pet. No weight restrictions. Some breed restrictions apply. Business Hours: Mon - Fri: 8:30 AM - 5:30 PM Sat: 10:00 AM - 5:00 PM Ready to Lease? Contact us for more information! show contact info Website: www.apt-rental.com?n=imt_alpharetta&rp=nVj3soufvup9&t=wb *Total Monthly Price includes base rent, all monthly mandatory and any user-selected optional fees. Excludes variable, usage-based, and required charges due at or prior to move-in or at move-out. Discounts, if applicable, will be calculated upon lease execution. Minimum lease terms and occupancy guidelines may apply. Deposits may vary based on credit, rental history, income, or other qualifying criteria. Additional fees and taxes may apply and will be disclosed per governing laws and company policies. Total Monthly Price may be displayed as a whole dollar amount for advertising purposes only; actual charges are calculated using exact fee amounts, including cents, and may vary from the displayed amount by up to 50 cents due to rounding. Price shown is Total Monthly Price including monthly mandatory fees* Monthly Mandatory Fees: - Package Locker: $5/month - Credit Reporting: $5/month - Water Charges: Varies - Sewer Charges: Varies - Pest: $4.50/month - Service Fee: $3.99/month - Trash Service: $10/month All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 991C828EC11A4782",
