        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post Brooks Crossing Apartments 8050 Taylor Road Riverdale, GA 30274 A wonderful home in Riverdale is waiting for you! Contact us for more information! show contact info We currently have a gorgeous 2 bedroom 2 bathroom with 1163 sq ft. Monthly Price: $1125 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Brooks Crossing Apartments boasts amenities that make living here both comfortable and convenient. Work out in our new fitness center, relax by the pool or enjoy the use of the multi-purpose sports court. We offer numerous tot lots for younger residents, and a spacious sunning deck perfect for grilling or picnicking. You can also enjoy a leisurely walk around the community as it is nestled among canopies of trees and other natural surroundings or update your social media status in our business center. $200 off your 1st month's rent Community Highlights: ŌłÆ Clubhouse ŌłÆ Courtyard ŌłÆ Fitness Center ŌłÆ Gated ŌłÆ Maintenance on site ŌłÆ Picnic Areas ŌłÆ Playground ŌłÆ Smoke Free ŌłÆ Sparkling Pool ŌłÆ Wi-Fi at Pool and Clubhouse ŌłÆ Fax/Copy Services ŌłÆ Laundry Facilities ŌłÆ Monthly Resident Events ŌłÆ Multi Use Room ŌłÆ Online Services ŌłÆ Package Service ŌłÆ Preferred Employer Discounts Available ŌłÆ Resident Referral Bonuses ŌłÆ Sports Courts ŌłÆ Tennis Court Apartment Home Highlights: ŌłÆ Air Conditioning ŌłÆ Cable Ready ŌłÆ Ceiling Fans ŌłÆ Deck ŌłÆ Dishwasher ŌłÆ Disposal ŌłÆ Fireplace ŌłÆ Freezer ŌłÆ Heating ŌłÆ High Speed Internet Access ŌłÆ Range ŌłÆ Refrigerator ŌłÆ Tub/Shower ŌłÆ Vaulted Ceilings ŌłÆ Walk-In Closets ŌłÆ Washer/Dryer Hookup ŌłÆ Wi-Fi ŌłÆ Window Coverings Contact us for more information! show contact info Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/brookscrossingapts Website: www.apt-rental.com?n=brooks_crossing&rp=t4PGZcyKT2qK&t=wb Online Application: www.apt-rental.com?n=brooks_crossing&rp=t4PGZcyKT2qK&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.apt-rental.com?n=brooks_crossing&rp=t4PGZcyKT2qK&t=sch Leasing Options: 6-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month Pet Policy: A maximum of 2 pet per unit shall be accepted. The pet fee is $300 Non-Refundable per pet. A pet addendum must be completed and pet fees must be paid prior to moving in. If there is more than one pet per unit, the combined weight of the 2 pets cannot exceed 50lbs. Monthly Pet Rent: $20 per pet All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY D6C0C42A524340",
