        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Grove Parkview Bedroom: 2 | Bathroom: 2 Square Footage: 961 sq ft Monthly Price: $1919 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Call us for more information! show contact info Community Description With our top notch location in the Gwinnett County School District, you have easy access to great schools and employers. Enjoy quick commutes to Mountain Park Elementary, UEI - Stone Mountain, Heatcraft Worldwide Refrigeration and Platinum Financial Services, or anywhere else your academic and career aspirations take you. Plus with great spots like Rewind Bistro & Lounge, Yellow River Wildlife Sanctuary, and Stone Mountain Park all nearby, you will never run out of new things to try! Community Amenities ŌØ¢ Fitness Center ŌØ¢ Lake Access ŌØ¢ Maintenance on site ŌØ¢ Playground ŌØ¢ Pool ŌØ¢ Property Manager on Site ŌØ¢ Car Care Station ŌØ¢ Coffee & Tea Bar ŌØ¢ Pergolas ŌØ¢ Rentable Storage Units ŌØ¢ Sports Court Apartment Features ŌØ¢ Air Conditioning ŌØ¢ Coat Closet ŌØ¢ Dishwasher ŌØ¢ Heating ŌØ¢ High Speed Internet Access ŌØ¢ Smoke Free ŌØ¢ Storage Space ŌØ¢ Walk-in Closets ŌØ¢ Washer/Dryer Hookup ŌØ¢ Breakfast Bar in Select Units ŌØ¢ Deck/ Patio in Select Units ŌØ¢ Ensuite Bathroom in Select Units ŌØ¢ Fireplace in Select Units ŌØ¢ Granite-Style Countertops in Select Units ŌØ¢ Outdoor Storage in Select Units ŌØ¢ Pantry in Select Units ŌØ¢ Sunroom in Select Units ŌØ¢ Upgraded Fixtures in Select Units ŌØ¢ Wood-Style Flooring in Select Units Contact Information Visit Us: 1900 Glenn Club Dr Stone Mountain, GA 30087 Call us for more information! show contact info Hours: Mon - Fri: 9:00 AM - 6:00 PM Sat: 10:00 AM - 5:00 PM Website: www.rentalsapts.com?n=grove_parkview&rp=w4m1C4fZjXft&t=wb Online Application: www.rentalsapts.com?n=grove_parkview&rp=w4m1C4fZjXft&t=ap Additional Details Pet Policy: Two pet max per apartment. - One-Time Fee: $350 for one pet $650 for two pets. - Monthly Pet Rent: $25 per pet. - Breed restrictions apply, but certified service animals (CSA) or emotional support animals (ESA) are exempt. Approved PetScreening profile required. Lease Terms: 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month, 13-Month, 14-Month, 15-Month, 16-Month, 17-Month, 18-Month All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 3C84TMG7K6SE92CX",
