        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post IMT Buckhead on 26th 225 26th St NW Atlanta, GA 30309 Monthly Price: $2605 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Bedrooms: 3 Bathrooms: 2 Square Footage: 1800 sq ft Call us for more information! show contact info Features in this apartment home: ŌØ¢ Air Conditioning ŌØ¢ Cable Ready ŌØ¢ Ceiling Fans ŌØ¢ Crown Molding ŌØ¢ Deck ŌØ¢ Dining Room ŌØ¢ Dishwasher ŌØ¢ Disposal ŌØ¢ Double Vanities ŌØ¢ Eat-in Kitchen ŌØ¢ High Speed Internet Access ŌØ¢ Instant Hot Water ŌØ¢ Island Kitchen ŌØ¢ Linen Closet ŌØ¢ Microwave ŌØ¢ Oven/Range ŌØ¢ Pantry ŌØ¢ Refrigerator/Freezer/Ice Maker ŌØ¢ Storage Units ŌØ¢ Trash Compactor ŌØ¢ Tub/Shower ŌØ¢ Vaulted Ceiling ŌØ¢ Views ŌØ¢ Walk-In Closets ŌØ¢ Wheelchair Accessible (Rooms) ŌØ¢ Window Coverings ŌØ¢ Black Appliances in Classic Home ŌØ¢ Double-Basin Sink with Pull-Down Sprayer in Upgraded Homes ŌØ¢ Fireplaces in Select Homes ŌØ¢ Granite Countertops in Classic Homes ŌØ¢ Hard Surface Countertops ŌØ¢ Individual Climate Control ŌØ¢ Plush Carpeting in Living Areas ŌØ¢ Skyline Views in Select Homes ŌØ¢ Stainless Steel Appliances in Upgraded Homes ŌØ¢ Tile Flooring in Classic Homes ŌØ¢ USB Port in Kitchen in Upgraded Homes ŌØ¢ Washers and Dryers in Select Homes ŌØ¢ White Ceiling Fans in Classic Homes About the community: Nestled between the Buckhead and Midtown areas of Atlanta, IMT Buckhead on 26th is all about the location. With easy access to I-75 & I-85, the urban landscape of Atlanta, GA is at your fingertips. The community offers a beautiful and modern southern retreat from the urban sprawl of Atlanta. From the outside, you are welcomed by an array of grouped buildings, all married together in a uniform fashion. You'll feel instantly at home when you see the myriad of amenities that await you at IMT Buckhead on 26th! Please copy and paste to take a video tour: https://liveimt.com/imtBuckheadYoutubeTour Price shown is Total Monthly Price including monthly mandatory fees* Monthly Mandatory Fees: - Package Locker: $5/month - Credit Reporting: $5/month - Service Fee: $6/month - Water Charges: Varies - Pest Fee: $5/month - Sewer Charges: Varies - Common Area Electricity: $10.33/month - Trash Charge: $15/month Amenities at our property: ŌØ¢ Bike Storage ŌØ¢ Courtyard ŌØ¢ Picnic Area ŌØ¢ Planned Social Activities ŌØ¢ Property Manager on Site ŌØ¢ Public Transportation ŌØ¢ Recycling ŌØ¢ Renters Insurance Program ŌØ¢ Storage Space ŌØ¢ Walking/Biking Trails ŌØ¢ Business / Conference Center ŌØ¢ Club Room ŌØ¢ Easy Access to I-75, I-85 and GA 400 ŌØ¢ Elevator Building(s) ŌØ¢ Fire Pit ŌØ¢ Outdoor Grilling Stations ŌØ¢ Outdoor Pool ŌØ¢ Pool Views in Select Homes ŌØ¢ Professionally Managed ŌØ¢ Resort-Style Clubhouse Additional information: Call us for more information! show contact info Terms: 3-Month, 4-Month, 5-Month, 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month Pets: At IMT Buckhead on 26th, we know that the path to your heart is marked with paw prints and that the best part of your day is coming home to a wagging tail. Pets are residents, too! $300 NON-REFUNDABLE PET FEE, PER PET $25 PET RENT, PER PET. No weight restriction. Some breed restrictions apply. Please call our Leasing Center for complete Pet Policy information. Website: www.apts-rental.com?n=imt_buckhead_on_26th&rp=v8A1pdxXTPjb&t=wb Please call us for complete parking information. *Total Monthly Price includes base rent, all monthly mandatory and any user-selected optional fees. Excludes variable, usage-based, and required charges due at or prior to move-in or at move-out. Discounts, if applicable, will be calculated upon lease execution. Minimum lease terms and occupancy guidelines may apply. Deposits may vary based on credit, rental history, income, or other qualifying criteria. Additional fees and taxes may apply and will be disclosed per governing laws and company policies. Total Monthly Price may be displayed as a whole dollar amount for advertising purposes only; actual charges are calculated using exact fee amounts, including cents, and may vary from the displayed amount by up to 50 cents due to rounding. Price shown is Total Monthly Price including monthly mandatory fees* Monthly Mandatory Fees: - Package Locker: $5/month - Credit Reporting: $5/month - Service Fee: $6/month - Water Charges: Varies - Pest Fee: $5/month - Sewer Charges: Varies - Common Area Electricity: $10.33/month - Trash Charge: $15/month All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 192DC3B85A724F09",
