        "mainpic": "1eef2e3d-607a-4496-906f-c1d3ffe30a67",
        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post Las Palmas Apartments 1 Seasons Pkwy Norcross, GA 30093 Apartment Information: 1 Bedroom | 1 Bath Apartment Size: 943 sq ft Monthly Price: $1064 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Lease Terms: 6-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month, 13-Month Property Description: Las Palmas Apartments 1 Seasons Pkwy Norcross, GA 30093 Tel├®fono: show contact info www.laspalmasatlanta.com Comodidades del Apartamento (Apartment Features) Descubre el Apartamento de tus sue├▒os! ? Cocina Equipada ? Barra de desayuno & ├ürea de comedor ? Conexiones para lavadora/secadora ? Aire Acondicionado ? Pisos Renovados ? Espacios amplios ? Patios/Balcones cubiertos ? Piscina estilo resort ? Gimnasio ? Centro de Negocios ? Parque de recreo ? Zona de P├Łcnic ? Instalaciones de Lavander├Ła ? Acceso Controlado ? Eventos para los residentes Nuestra Comunidad (About our Community) ┬┐Est├Īs buscando apartamento de una, dos o tres rec├Īmaras? Situado en Seasons Pkwy al lado de Dawson Boulevard en Norcross, GA. Excelente ubicaci├│n, muy cerca de I-85, restaurantes, centros comerciales, supermercados, escuelas y a tan solo 20 minutos de Midtown Atlanta. Urbanizaci├│n privada con acceso controlado (gated community), piscina, gimnasio y lavander├Ła. ┬ĪSolicita tu apartamento! Tarifa Solicitud $75 (por solicitante) Tarifa Administrativa $165 (por apartamento) Dep├│sito de Seguridad $400 Tarifa de Gesti├│n de Riesgos (en caso sea aplicable) *Las tarifas de solicitud y administrativa no son reembolsables. Website: www.apt-rental.com?n=las_palmas_apartments&rp=hqfhkb&t=wb Application: www.apt-rental.com?n=las_palmas_apartments&rp=hqfhkb&t=ap ┬ĪLl├Īmanos al show contact info y ven a vernos! Hablamos Espa├▒ol. Equal Housing Opportunity Website: www.lease-apts.com?n=las_palmas&rp=2QYC5EyX5Vdy&t=wb Call us today! show contact info Mon - Fri: 8:30 AM - 5:30 PM Sat: 10:00 AM - 5:00 PM Pet Ownership Policy: A maximum of 2 pet per unit shall be accepted. The pet fee is $315 Non-Refundable per pet. Monthly Pet Rent of $25. A pet addendum must be completed, and pet fees must be paid prior to moving in. If there is more than one pet per unit, the combined weight of the 2 pets cannot exceed 50lbs. Proudly managed by Ventron Management Application fee is $75 and Admin Fee is $165 (both are non-refundable). All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY D8D9640CEC6947EC",
