        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Las Palmas Apartments Visit Our Community Today! 1 Seasons Pkwy Norcross, GA 30093 Las Palmas Apartments Leasing Office: 1 Seasons Pkwy Norcross, GA 30093 Contact Info: show contact info Take a look at what Las Palmas Apartments has to offer! Amenities available to residents at Las Palmas Apartments include a brand-new fitness center with virtual enhanced cardio equipment, an abdominal area, and a multi-weight station. A tot area for the younger residents is on the premises, along with a business center where you can update your social media status. Las Palmas Apartments has Wi-Fi throughout the community so you can stay connected while doing laundry or relaxing by the sparkling serene poolside. A lighted tennis court and playground area are also available to residents. And don't forget about your four-legged friends-Las Palmas is pet-friendly, although breed restrictions apply. Lease Terms: 6-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month, 13-Month Apartment Amenities: Carpet Dishwasher Disposal/Trash Compactor Eat-in Kitchen High-Speed Internet Access Oven Patios or Balconies Range Refrigerator/Freezer Tub/Shower Custom Lighting Designer Touches Fireplaces in Select Apartment Homes Full-Size Washer Dryer Connections Hardwood Floors Premier Upgrade Unit Spacious Layouts Storage Units Total Electric Walk-In Closets Community Amenities: Business Center Fitness Center with Cardio Screens Full-Size Washer Dryer Connections Gated Community Picnic Area Playground Smoke-Free Sparkling Pool Tennis Court Great Location Online Services Pets Allowed Preferred Employer Discounts Available Resident Social Events Screened-In Patios Serene Views Leasing Hours: Mon - Fri: 8:30 AM - 5:30 PM Sat: 10:00 AM - 5:00 PM Pet Policy: A maximum of 2 pets per unit is accepted. The pet fee is $315 (non-refundable) per pet, with a monthly pet rent of $25. A pet addendum must be completed, and pet fees must be paid prior to moving in. If there is more than one pet, the combined weight of both pets cannot exceed 50 lbs. Contact Info: show contact info Website: www.apt-rental.com?n=las_palmas_apartments&rp=hqfhkb&t=wb Application: www.apt-rental.com?n=las_palmas_apartments&rp=hqfhkb&t=ap Application Fee: $75 (non-refundable) Admin Fee: $165 (non-refundable) Prices and availability are subject to change. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY Bedrooms: 2 | Bathrooms: 2 Square Footage: 1195 sq ft Monthly Price: $1154 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Website: www.lease-apts.com?n=las_palmas&rp=otrHGYj6L95h&t=wb Phone-Number: show contact info Pet-Policy: A maximum of 2 pet per unit shall be accepted. The pet fee is $315 Non-Refundable per pet. Monthly Pet Rent of $25. A pet addendum must be completed, and pet fees must be paid prior to moving in. If there is more than one pet per unit, the combined weight of the 2 pets cannot exceed 50lbs. Lease-Length: 6-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month, 13-Month Call for Directions Application fee is $75 and Admin Fee is $165 (both are non-refundable). All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY FB67C517E5B945C3",
