, the combined weight of both pets cannot exceed 50 lbs. Contact Info: show contact info Website: www.apt-rental.com?n=las_palmas_apartments&rp=hqfhkb&t=wb Application: www.apt-rental.com?n=las_palmas_apartments&rp=hqfhkb&t=ap Application Fee: $75 (non-refundable) Admin Fee: $165 (non-refundable) Prices and availability are subject to change. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY Bedrooms: 2 | Bathrooms: 2 Square Footage: 1195 sq ft Monthly Price: $1154 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Website: www.lease-apts.com?n=las_palmas&rp=otrHGYj6L95h&t=wb Phone-Number: show contact info Pet-Policy: A maximum of 2 pet per unit shall be accepted. The pet fee is $315 Non-Refundable per pet. Monthly Pet Rent of $25. A pet addendum must be completed, and pet fees must be paid prior to moving in. If there is more than one pet per unit, the combined weight of the 2 pets cannot exceed 50lbs. Lease-Length: 6-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month, 13-Month Call for Directions Application fee is $75 and Admin Fee is $165 (both are non-refundable). All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY FB67C517E5B945C3",
