        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post Magnolia at Whitlock - A place to call home! Bed: 2 / Bath: 1 Sq. Footage: 1015 sq ft Monthly Price: $1150 - $1565 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Terms: 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month, 13-Month, 14-Month Call us for more information! show contact info Magnolia at Whitlock offers spacious, move-in-ready homes with updated interiors and modern finishes. Each apartment is designed for comfort, with features that make settling in easy from day one. It's a fresh start in a quiet, well-connected Marietta neighborhood. Our Apartment Homes Feature: ŌŚÅ Air Conditioner ŌŚÅ Ceiling Fan in select units ŌŚÅ Oversized Living Areas ŌŚÅ Plush Carpeting ŌŚÅ Pool View ŌŚÅ Top Floor ŌŚÅ Valet trash ŌŚÅ W/D Hookup ŌŚÅ Wall-to-wall carpet ŌŚÅ Washer/Dryer* ŌŚÅ Ample Closet Space ŌŚÅ Central heat and air conditioning ŌŚÅ Extra Storage Available ŌŚÅ Fully Equipped Kitchen ŌŚÅ Spacious balcony or enclosed private patio Our Residents Enjoy: ŌŚÅ 24-7 Emergency Maintenance ŌŚÅ Brand New Resident Clubroom ŌŚÅ Business Center/WiFi Bar ŌŚÅ Free Weights ŌŚÅ Outdoor Grilling &amp Picnic Area ŌŚÅ Pet Friendly ŌŚÅ Pet Wash ŌŚÅ Smart Cardio Equipment ŌŚÅ State-of-the-Art Fitness Center ŌŚÅ Valet Trash Service ŌŚÅ 15 Minutes to Lockheed and Dobbins Air Force Base ŌŚÅ Brand New Fully-Renovated Clubhouse ŌŚÅ Minutes to Historic Marietta Square ŌŚÅ Onsite Professional Management Team ŌŚÅ Resort-Style Swimming Pool with Sun Soaked Seating Call us for more information! show contact info 925 Whitlock Ave. NW Marietta, GA 30064 Website: www.apts-rental.com?n=magnolia_at_whitlock&rp=scwXm2U1kBSd&t=wb Online Application: www.apts-rental.com?n=magnolia_at_whitlock&rp=scwXm2U1kBSd&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.apts-rental.com?n=magnolia_at_whitlock&rp=scwXm2U1kBSd&t=sch Mon - Fri: 9:00 AM - 5:00 PM Pets: Pet Guidelines Allowed pets include dogs, cats, fish, birds, and hamsters Pet fees or pet rent apply to dogs and cats only Up to two pets per home Exotic pets or livestock are not permitted Fish tanks may not exceed 24 gallons Breed Restrictions For more information on restrictions or pet-related fees, contact our leasing team. We're happy to help you and your pets find the purr-fect fit! Administrative Fee $100 All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY AVV6XE4GM4B601K8",
