        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post Welcome home to East Perimeter Pointe Apartments! Located at: 4946 Snapfinger Woods Dr. Decatur, GA 30035 Rental Information: # of Bedrooms: 1 # of Bathrooms: 1 Square Footage: 555 sq ft Monthly Price: $888 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Phone: show contact info Get ready for a refreshing new take on apartment living, at East Perimeter Pointe. These newly renovated apartments in Decatur, GA offer the pinnacle of comfort, convenience, and style, with spacious and streamlined 1- and 2-bedroom floor plans, top-notch amenities and a wonderful location just 20 minutes east of downtown Atlanta along I-20. Each of our dynamic and inviting apartment homes is smartly appointed with upgraded lighting packages, sunrooms, and custom paint tones, all of which work together to create a homey and inspiring environment. Our amenities list is the envy of Decatur, featuring both indoor and outdoor pools, lighted tennis courts, and a cardio and fitness center, among many other enticing attractions. Community Features: ŌŚŠ Accepts Electronic Payments ŌŚŠ Community Events ŌŚŠ Community/Onsite Parking ŌŚŠ Emergency Maintenance ŌŚŠ Fax/Copy Services ŌŚŠ Organized Activities ŌŚŠ Property Manager on Site ŌŚŠ Swimming Pool ŌŚŠ Tennis Court(s) ŌŚŠ Valet Trash ŌŚŠ Electronic Rent Payment ŌŚŠ Gazebo & Grilling Areas ŌŚŠ Monthly Resident Events ŌŚŠ On-site Maintenance Management ŌŚŠ Preferred Employer Discounts Available ŌŚŠ Public Transportation ŌŚŠ Racquetball Court(s) ŌŚŠ Resident Referral Bonuses ŌŚŠ Trail, Bike, Hike, Jog Apartment Home Features: ŌŚŠ Air Conditioning ŌŚŠ Breakfast Bar ŌŚŠ Cable Ready ŌŚŠ Cozy Fireplaces ŌŚŠ Custom Paint Tone ŌŚŠ Garbage Disposal ŌŚŠ Island Kitchens ŌŚŠ Linen Closet ŌŚŠ Smoke Free ŌŚŠ Storage Units ŌŚŠ Fully Equipped Kitchens w/Frost-Free Refrigerator ŌŚŠ Hardwood Flooring ŌŚŠ Newly Renovated Apartments ŌŚŠ Patio or Balcony Options ŌŚŠ Roommate Floor Plans ŌŚŠ Townhomes Available ŌŚŠ Upgraded Lighting Package Office Hours: Mon - Thu: 8:30 AM - 5:30 PM Fri: 9:00 AM - 5:30 PM Sat: 10:00 AM - 5:00 PM Phone: show contact info Pet Policy: A maximum of 2 pet per unit shall be accepted. The pet fee is $315 Non-Refundable per pet. A pet addendum must be completed and pet fees must be paid prior to moving in. If there is more than one pet per unit, the combined weight of the 2 pets cannot exceed 50lbs. Monthly Pet Rent of $20. For more information, please call our leasing office. Leasing Options: 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month, 13-Month Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/EastPerimeterPointe Website: www.rentalsapts.com?n=east_perimeter_pointe&rp=26hozGJsm9i4&t=wb Online Application: www.rentalsapts.com?n=east_perimeter_pointe&rp=26hozGJsm9i4&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.rentalsapts.com?n=east_perimeter_pointe&rp=26hozGJsm9i4&t=sch All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 2640529D7B6F4567",
