        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post RENTAL INFO Monthly Price: $1338 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Brookside Park Apartments: 565 Saint Johns Ave Sw Atlanta, GA 30315 Apartment for Rent: 1-BR 1-BA | Square Feet: 830 sq ft | Lease Length: 6-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month Phone: show contact info PROPERTY AMENITIES ŌŚÅ BBQ/Picnic Area ŌŚÅ Business Center ŌŚÅ Conference Room ŌŚÅ Fitness Center ŌŚÅ Monthly Resident Events ŌŚÅ Pet Care ŌŚÅ Planned Social Activities ŌŚÅ Property Manager on Site ŌŚÅ Terrace Level ŌŚÅ Wi-Fi at Pool and Clubhouse ŌŚÅ Access to Marta ŌŚÅ Clothes Care Center ŌŚÅ Custom Paint Tone ŌŚÅ Maintenance on site ŌŚÅ Package Service ŌŚÅ Picnic Areas and Gazebo ŌŚÅ Preferred Employer Discounts Available ŌŚÅ Public Transportation ŌŚÅ Resort Inspired Pool ŌŚÅ Roommate Style Floor Plans Available APARTMENT AMENITIES ŌŚÅ Cable Ready ŌŚÅ Carpet ŌŚÅ Dishwasher ŌŚÅ Multi Use Room ŌŚÅ Oven ŌŚÅ Range ŌŚÅ Walk-In Closets ŌŚÅ Washer/Dryer Hookup ŌŚÅ Wi-Fi ŌŚÅ Window Coverings ŌŚÅ Brushed Nickel Lighting ŌŚÅ Eat-in Kitchen ŌŚÅ Fully Equipped Kitchens ŌŚÅ Handrails ŌŚÅ High Speed Internet Access ŌŚÅ Intrusion alarms ŌŚÅ Refrigerator/Freezer ŌŚÅ Renovated Suites Available ŌŚÅ Total Electric ŌŚÅ Upgrade Complete ADDITIONAL INFO Description: Work out in our newly revamped fitness center or simply relax by the pool. You can also play a game of tennis at our tennis courts, or update your social media status in our business center. We invite you to call us for more information or come by and see why our residents choose to call Brookside Park home! We look forward to showing you around our community. Pet Policy: Brookside Park Apartments is a pet friendly community that welcome two pets per apartment home. The pet fee is $325 non-refundable per pet. There is a $20 monthly pet rent. A pet addendum must be completed, and pet fees must be paid prior to moving in. If there is more than one pet per unit, the combined weight of the 2 pets cannot exceed 50 lbs. Breed restrictions may apply. Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/brooksideparkatlanta Website: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=brookside_park&rp=owFJmm82xbhk&t=wb Online Application: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=brookside_park&rp=owFJmm82xbhk&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=brookside_park&rp=owFJmm82xbhk&t=sch Phone: show contact info All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 331DCF95D1CD4C",
