        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post Spring Lake Apartments, located at 7000 Southlake Pkwy Morrow, GA 30260. Call Today! show contact info Description ........ Spring Lake Apartments is in a fabulous location. Not only are we within minutes from Clayton State University, but we are also minutes from Southlake Mall, Piedmont Henry Hospital, Gillem Logistics Center, and numerous shops and restaurants. We are only a few miles from major interstates and a short commute to Downtown Atlanta. Bedrooms ........... 1 Bathrooms ......... 1 Sq Footage ......... 842 sq ft Monthly Price: $1283 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Lease Term ........ 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month Amenity List ...... Ō×ó Clothes Care Center Ō×ó Clubhouse w/WIFI Ō×ó Clubroom Ō×ó Courtyard Ō×ó Fitness Center Ō×ó Package Receiving Ō×ó Pet Care Ō×ó Waterfront Ō×ó Community Playground Ō×ó Flexible Lease Terms Ō×ó Maintenance on site Ō×ó Picnic Areas & Gazebos Ō×ó Picnic Pavilion with Grills Ō×ó Relaxing Community Lake Ō×ó Relaxing Community Lake & Pavilion Ō×ó Resort Inspired Pool Apartment Home Features ..... Ō×ó Balcony/Patio Ō×ó Custom Paint Tone Ō×ó Dishwasher Ō×ó Disposal Ō×ó Fireplace Ō×ó Lake views Ō×ó Oven/Range Ō×ó Spacious Sunrooms Ō×ó W/D Connections Ō×ó Walk-In Closets Ō×ó Air Conditioning and Heating Ō×ó Brushed Nickel Hardware Ō×ó Brushed Nickel Lighting Ō×ó Ceiling Fans with Lighting Ō×ó Classic Two-Tone Paint Ō×ó Fully Equipped Kitchens Ō×ó Refrigerator and Freezer/Ice Maker Ō×ó Renovated Suites Available Ō×ó Roommate Style Floor Plans Available Ō×ó Separate Dining Areas Our Pet Policy ... Spring Lake Apartments is a pet-friendly community that welcomes two pets per apartment home. The pet fee is $300 non-refundable per pet. Monthly Pet Rent is $25. A pet addendum must be completed, and pet fees must be paid prior to moving in. If there is more than one pet per unit, the combined weight of the 2 pets cannot exceed 50 lbs. Breed restrictions may apply. Leasing Hours ... Mon - Fri: 8:30 AM - 5:30 PM Sat: 10:00 AM - 5:00 PM Call Today! show contact info Our Location ..... 7000 Southlake Pkwy Morrow, GA 30260 Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/springlakeatl Website: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=spring_lake&rp=7k4LhW2B5W6k&t=wb Online Application: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=spring_lake&rp=7k4LhW2B5W6k&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=spring_lake&rp=7k4LhW2B5W6k&t=sch All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 2D88E72A5CD94D0",
