e) Admin Fee: $165 (non-refundable) Prices and availability are subject to change. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY Website: www.lease-apts.com?n=las_palmas&rp=eYSD5jcLguBP&t=wb Call us today! show contact info Mon - Fri: 8:30 AM - 5:30 PM Sat: 10:00 AM - 5:00 PM Pet Ownership Policy: A maximum of 2 pet per unit shall be accepted. The pet fee is $315 Non-Refundable per pet. Monthly Pet Rent of $25. A pet addendum must be completed, and pet fees must be paid prior to moving in. If there is more than one pet per unit, the combined weight of the 2 pets cannot exceed 50lbs. Proudly managed by Ventron Management Application fee is $75 and Admin Fee is $165 (both are non-refundable). All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 93DA064AB4B44115",
