        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post Highland Willows 6071 Highway 85 Riverdale, GA 30274 Monthly Price: $1100 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Bedrooms: 2 Bathrooms: 2 Square Footage: 1000 sq ft Contact Info: show contact info Features in this apartment home: Ō×ó Air Conditioning Ō×ó Cable Ready Ō×ó Ceiling Fan(s) Ō×ó Dishwasher Ō×ó Extra Storage Ō×ó Hardwood Flooring Ō×ó Patio Ō×ó Refrigerator Ō×ó Washer Dryer Connections About the community: Come home to Highland Willows Apartments and enjoy a new way of life! Our staff is dedicated to providing quality, professional and courteous service to our residents. Conveniently located minutes from I285, I85, I75, Hartsfield Jackson Airport and Downtown Atlanta. Choose from 1, 2 and 3 bedroom, garden style apartments and 2 bedroom town home apartments with private patios. Highland Willows is not just another apartment community, It's home! Amenities at our property: Ō×ó Accepts Electronic Payments Ō×ó Emergency Maintenance Ō×ó Extra Storage Ō×ó Laundry Facility Ō×ó On Site Maintenance Ō×ó On Site Management Ō×ó On Site Patrol Ō×ó Pet Friendly Ō×ó Playground Ō×ó Swimming Pool Additional information: Contact Info: show contact info Terms: 6-Month, 12-Month Pets: Max Number of Pets: 2 One-Time Pet Fee: $300 Non-refundable Max Weight: 30lbs Pet Policy Restrictions: Weight and breed restrictions apply. Please contact the leasing office for more details. Website: www.apts-rental.com?n=highland_willows&rp=9m5gqRc34x6b&t=wb Online Application: www.apts-rental.com?n=highland_willows&rp=9m5gqRc34x6b&t=ap 3D Virtual Tour: www.apts-rental.com?n=highland_willows&rp=9m5gqRc34x6b&t=trt Schedule a Tour: www.apts-rental.com?n=highland_willows&rp=9m5gqRc34x6b&t=sch All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY DGB1DN1RMLNGTG",
