nal and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Lease Terms: 6-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month, 13-Month Leasing Hours: Mon - Fri: 8:30 AM - 5:30 PM Sat: 10:00 AM - 5:00 PM Pet Policy: A maximum of 2 pet per unit shall be accepted. The pet fee is $315 Non-Refundable per pet. Monthly Pet Rent of $25. A pet addendum must be completed, and pet fees must be paid prior to moving in. If there is more than one pet per unit, the combined weight of the 2 pets cannot exceed 50lbs. Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/LasPalmasAtlanta Website: www.lease-apts.com?n=las_palmas&rp=3SUnn758recT&t=wb Management Company: Ventron Management Application fee is $75 and Admin Fee is $165 (both are non-refundable). All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 89D6CD23349640F6",
