oving in. If there is more than one pet per unit, the combined weight of both pets cannot exceed 50 lbs. Website: www.apt-rental.com?n=las_palmas_apartments&rp=hqfhkb&t=wb Application: www.apt-rental.com?n=las_palmas_apartments&rp=hqfhkb&t=ap Contact: show contact info Application Fee: $75 (non-refundable) Admin Fee: $165 (non-refundable) Prices and availability are subject to change. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY Call or visit our website to schedule a personal tour! Office Phone: show contact info Mon - Fri: 8:30 AM - 5:30 PM Sat: 10:00 AM - 5:00 PM Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/LasPalmasAtlanta Website: www.apts-rental.com?n=las_palmas&rp=h2HdeHV96mzo&t=wb Property Management: Ventron Management Application fee is $75 and Admin Fee is $165 (both are non-refundable). All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY FB67C517E5B945C3",
