        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post Las Palmas Apartments Visit our community today! 1 Seasons Pkwy Norcross, GA 30093 Monthly Price: $1154 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Apartment Type: 2-BR 2-BA Apartment Size: 1195 sq ft Lease Terms: 6-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month, 13-Month Pet Policy: A maximum of 2 pet per unit shall be accepted. The pet fee is $315 Non-Refundable per pet. Monthly Pet Rent of $25. A pet addendum must be completed, and pet fees must be paid prior to moving in. If there is more than one pet per unit, the combined weight of the 2 pets cannot exceed 50lbs. Description: Las Palmas Apartments Lease Length: 6-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month, 13-Month Contact: show contact info Property Amenities Business Center Fitness Center with Cardio Screens Full Size Washer Dryer Connections Gated Community Picnic Area Playground Smoke-Free Sparkling Pool Tennis Court Great Location Online Services Pets Allowed Preferred Employer Discounts Available Resident Social Events Screened-In Patios Serene Views Apartment Amenities Carpet Dishwasher Disposal/Trash Compactor Eat-in Kitchen High-Speed Internet Access Oven Patios or Balconies Range Refrigerator/Freezer Tub/Shower Custom Lighting Designer Touches Fireplaces in Select Apartment Homes Full-Size Washer Dryer Connections Hardwood Floors Premier Upgrade Unit Spacious Layouts Storage Units Total Electric Walk-In Closets Additional Info Description: Las Palmas Apartments is only minutes from shopping and dining, Gwinnett Arena, Emory Hospital, Perimeter Mall, and downtown Atlanta. Its location makes commuting to Gwinnett County, Stone Mountain, and numerous areas very convenient due to its proximity to I85 and I285. Pet Policy: A maximum of 2 pets per unit is accepted. The pet fee is $315 (non-refundable) per pet, with a monthly pet rent of $25. A pet addendum must be completed, and pet fees must be paid prior to moving in. If there is more than one pet per unit, the combined weight of both pets cannot exceed 50 lbs. Website: www.apt-rental.com?n=las_palmas_apartments&rp=hqfhkb&t=wb Application: www.apt-rental.com?n=las_palmas_apartments&rp=hqfhkb&t=ap Contact: show contact info Application Fee: $75 (non-refundable) Admin Fee: $165 (non-refundable) Prices and availability are subject to change. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY Call or visit our website to schedule a personal tour! Office Phone: show contact info Mon - Fri: 8:30 AM - 5:30 PM Sat: 10:00 AM - 5:00 PM Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/LasPalmasAtlanta Website: www.apts-rental.com?n=las_palmas&rp=h2HdeHV96mzo&t=wb Property Management: Ventron Management Application fee is $75 and Admin Fee is $165 (both are non-refundable). All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY FB67C517E5B945C3",
