        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Now $1695! Open Sun July 12th 2-4p \"Enjoy Intown Living in a Quiet Forest-Like Setting\" *Text show contact info for an appointment Enjoy living in the \"Heart of the City of Decatur 30030\" within an easy walk to Cafes, Eateries and Festivals on Decatur Square. Children's Healthcare 6mi and we are also located in the Excellent City of Decatur School District! This \"Spacious Unit\" is located in a small community of only 22 units. Each building has 4-units 2-up and 2 down. Those who value living in a \"Quiet Place\" will love it! We've included our \"Leasing Guidelines\" below for your convenience. 2br+1.5ba Gleaming New Oak Hardwood Floors, Breakfast Bar, Black Ceiling Fans in both Bedrooms Central Heat + Air, Spacious Walk-In Closets, Balcony, Ceramic Tile Baths, Window Treatments and More! Convenient to: Downtown Atlanta, Intown, Midtown, Virginia Highland, Highlands, Old Fourth Ward, 4th, CDC, Druid Hills, Children's Healthcare, Ponce City Market, East Atlanta, East Lake, Tucker, Lithonia, Stone Mountain and more! Tenants pay all utilities water, gas, electric and cable. Laundry room located inside the building so there's no need to go outside For your security please note that is a \"Secure Entry \" Only tenants have access to main entry door *Must have Good Credit (690+) and Good Refs. and Verifiable Rental History. Lower credit score = less than 650 will require a higher security deposit. We may, at our discretion consider scores less than 650 if and Only if this is being caused by medical debt or student loan debt. Please bring a copy of your credit report with credit score and along with your 2 most recent pay stubs we will take a preliminary look at your situation without charging you an application fee. You must earn at least 3x's the rent to qualify. Pet Friendly for Cats Only. Pet Fee $250 for 1 cat or $300 for 2 cats + $10 per month pet rent. *Text Only: include your name, occupation, how many people, pets? and when you. need to move. Credit scores less than 650 may require an additional deposit. Scores less than 650 will not be accepted. Serious applicants should bring a copy of their credit report and 2 most recent pay stubs. Gross income should be about 3x's the rent. This is a Quiet Community of Respectful, Kind and Quiet Neighbors. Quiet Neighbors want Quiet Neighbors. *If you are seriously interested please bring a Money Order for $75 per person over 18 yrs.for the Application Fee, A copy of your credit report with credit score ( get one at creditkarma.com) 2 most recent check stubs, a copy of your driver's license and a copy of your work or school i.d. Please note that additional information may be required. If there is not Open House posted, please text for an appointment to see the unit. Property Manager is a Licensed Real Estate Agent in the State of Georgia and Holds an Interest in the property.",
