      "house_ger": {
        "id": "a9a09c09-7633-42c3-b10e-b7d0b8032076",
        "name": "Luxury living at East Perimeter Pointe Apartments! 1 BD / 1 BA availab",
        "location": "4946 Snapfinger Woods Dr.",
        "mainpic": "b8b45dd5-b78c-4724-9f97-e87df10fa0c1",
        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post East Perimeter Pointe Apartments Located at: 4946 Snapfinger Woods Dr. Decatur, GA 30035 Featured apartment home: 1 bed | 1 bath | 770 - 889 sq ft Monthly Price: $973 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Call us for more information! show contact info Get ready for a refreshing new take on apartment living, at East Perimeter Pointe. These newly renovated apartments in Decatur, GA offer the pinnacle of comfort, convenience, and style, with spacious and streamlined 1- and 2-bedroom floor plans, top-notch amenities and a wonderful location just 20 minutes east of downtown Atlanta along I-20. Each of our dynamic and inviting apartment homes is smartly appointed with upgraded lighting packages, sunrooms, and custom paint tones, all of which work together to create a homey and inspiring environment. Our amenities list is the envy of Decatur, featuring both indoor and outdoor pools, lighted tennis courts, and a cardio and fitness center, among many other enticing attractions. Wonderful Amenities! ŌŚÅ 24 Hour Availability ŌŚÅ Business Center ŌŚÅ Community Events ŌŚÅ Emergency Maintenance ŌŚÅ Green Community ŌŚÅ Laundry Facilities ŌŚÅ On-Site Maintenance ŌŚÅ Organized Activities ŌŚÅ Playground ŌŚÅ Storage Space ŌŚÅ Electronic Rent Payment ŌŚÅ Gazebo & Grilling Areas ŌŚÅ Monthly Resident Events ŌŚÅ On-site Maintenance Management ŌŚÅ Preferred Employer Discounts Available ŌŚÅ Public Transportation ŌŚÅ Racquetball Court(s) ŌŚÅ Resident Referral Bonuses ŌŚÅ Trail, Bike, Hike, Jog Apartment Features! ŌŚÅ Air Conditioning ŌŚÅ Breakfast Bar ŌŚÅ Cable Ready ŌŚÅ Cozy Fireplaces ŌŚÅ Dining Room ŌŚÅ Dishwasher ŌŚÅ Garbage Disposal ŌŚÅ Linen Closet ŌŚÅ Smoke Free ŌŚÅ Storage Units ŌŚÅ Fully Equipped Kitchens w/Frost-Free Refrigerator ŌŚÅ Hardwood Flooring ŌŚÅ Newly Renovated Apartments ŌŚÅ Patio or Balcony Options ŌŚÅ Roommate Floor Plans ŌŚÅ Townhomes Available ŌŚÅ Upgraded Lighting Package ŌŚÅ Washer & Dryer Connections Hours: Mon - Thu: 8:30 AM - 5:30 PM Fri: 9:00 AM - 5:30 PM Sat: 10:00 AM - 5:00 PM Call us for more information! show contact info Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/EastPerimeterPointe Website: www.apt-rental.com?n=east_perimeter_pointe&rp=gQy55rApjadm&t=wb Online Application: www.apt-rental.com?n=east_perimeter_pointe&rp=gQy55rApjadm&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.apt-rental.com?n=east_perimeter_pointe&rp=gQy55rApjadm&t=sch Terms: 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month, 13-Month Pet Policy: A maximum of 2 pet per unit shall be accepted. The pet fee is $315 Non-Refundable per pet. A pet addendum must be completed and pet fees must be paid prior to moving in. If there is more than one pet per unit, the combined weight of the 2 pets cannot exceed 50lbs. Monthly Pet Rent of $20. For more information, please call our leasing office. All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY C12E7C9B78AD474E",
