aturing both indoor and outdoor pools, lighted tennis courts, and a cardio and fitness center, among many other enticing attractions. Pet Policy: A maximum of 2 pet per unit shall be accepted. The pet fee is $315 Non-Refundable per pet. A pet addendum must be completed and pet fees must be paid prior to moving in. If there is more than one pet per unit, the combined weight of the 2 pets cannot exceed 50lbs. Monthly Pet Rent of $20. For more information, please call our leasing office. Call us for more information! show contact info Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/EastPerimeterPointe Website: www.apt-rental.com?n=east_perimeter_pointe&rp=6s7NAErEQ2X8&t=wb Online Application: www.apt-rental.com?n=east_perimeter_pointe&rp=6s7NAErEQ2X8&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.apt-rental.com?n=east_perimeter_pointe&rp=6s7NAErEQ2X8&t=sch All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 2640529D7B6F4567",
