        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post East Perimeter Pointe Apartments 4946 Snapfinger Woods Dr. Decatur, GA 30035 Call us at show contact info Apartment Information: 1 Bedroom | 1 Bath Apartment Size: 619 - 636 sq ft Monthly Price: $792 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Lease Terms: 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month, 13-Month Apartment Includes: ŌŚÅ Breakfast Bar ŌŚÅ Cable Ready ŌŚÅ Cozy Fireplaces ŌŚÅ Custom Paint Tone ŌŚÅ Dining Room ŌŚÅ Dishwasher ŌŚÅ Garbage Disposal ŌŚÅ Island Kitchens ŌŚÅ Linen Closet ŌŚÅ Storage Units ŌŚÅ Fully Equipped Kitchens w/Frost-Free Refrigerator ŌŚÅ Hardwood Flooring ŌŚÅ Newly Renovated Apartments ŌŚÅ Patio or Balcony Options ŌŚÅ Roommate Floor Plans ŌŚÅ Townhomes Available ŌŚÅ Upgraded Lighting Package Property Description: Get ready for a refreshing new take on apartment living, at East Perimeter Pointe. These newly renovated apartments in Decatur, GA offer the pinnacle of comfort, convenience, and style, with spacious and streamlined 1- and 2-bedroom floor plans, top-notch amenities and a wonderful location just 20 minutes east of downtown Atlanta along I-20. Each of our dynamic and inviting apartment homes is smartly appointed with upgraded lighting packages, sunrooms, and custom paint tones, all of which work together to create a homey and inspiring environment. Our amenities list is the envy of Decatur, featuring both indoor and outdoor pools, lighted tennis courts, and a cardio and fitness center, among many other enticing attractions. Property Amenities: ŌŚÅ Business Center ŌŚÅ Community/Onsite Parking ŌŚÅ Emergency Maintenance ŌŚÅ Fitness Center ŌŚÅ Gated Access ŌŚÅ Green Community ŌŚÅ Onsite Management ŌŚÅ Organized Activities ŌŚÅ Public Transportation ŌŚÅ Tennis Court(s) ŌŚÅ Electronic Rent Payment ŌŚÅ Gazebo & Grilling Areas ŌŚÅ Monthly Resident Events ŌŚÅ On-site Maintenance Management ŌŚÅ Preferred Employer Discounts Available ŌŚÅ Public Transportation ŌŚÅ Racquetball Court(s) ŌŚÅ Resident Referral Bonuses ŌŚÅ Trail, Bike, Hike, Jog Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/EastPerimeterPointe Website: www.apt-rental.com?n=east_perimeter_pointe&rp=ohYuj3zYi9SL&t=wb Online Application: www.apt-rental.com?n=east_perimeter_pointe&rp=ohYuj3zYi9SL&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.apt-rental.com?n=east_perimeter_pointe&rp=ohYuj3zYi9SL&t=sch Call us at show contact info Mon - Thu: 8:30 AM - 5:30 PM Fri: 9:00 AM - 5:30 PM Sat: 10:00 AM - 5:00 PM Pet Ownership Policy: A maximum of 2 pet per unit shall be accepted. The pet fee is $315 Non-Refundable per pet. A pet addendum must be completed and pet fees must be paid prior to moving in. If there is more than one pet per unit, the combined weight of the 2 pets cannot exceed 50lbs. Monthly Pet Rent of $20. For more information, please call our leasing office. All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY DE2F7F100D004448",
