        "geocode_query": "1900 Glenn Club Dr",
        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Come home to a great community - Grove Parkview! Address: 1900 Glenn Club Dr Stone Mountain, GA 30087 Call our office at show contact info Beds: Studio / Baths: 1 / Size: 641 sq ft Monthly Price: $1269 - $1499 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. At Grove Parkview Apartments, we embrace comfort, convenience, and style. Come home to spacious kitchens with quality features and chic, wood-inspired flooring in our studio, one, two, and three-bedroom apartments. Our exclusive community amenities are designed to elevate your living experience. Take a dip in our refreshing swimming pool, crush a workout in our 24-hour fitness center, or sit back and relax in our resident lounge. Plus, for your convenience, we offer off-street parking and a car care station! Deposit: Call Length of Lease: 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month, 13-Month, 14-Month, 15-Month, 16-Month, 17-Month, 18-Month Property Features: Ō×ó Fitness Center Ō×ó Lake Access Ō×ó Maintenance on site Ō×ó Playground Ō×ó Pool Ō×ó Property Manager on Site Ō×ó Car Care Station Ō×ó Coffee & Tea Bar Ō×ó Pergolas Ō×ó Rentable Storage Units Ō×ó Sports Court Apartment Amenities: Ō×ó Air Conditioning Ō×ó Coat Closet Ō×ó Dishwasher Ō×ó Heating Ō×ó High Speed Internet Access Ō×ó Smoke Free Ō×ó Storage Space Ō×ó Walk-in Closets Ō×ó Washer/Dryer Hookup Ō×ó Breakfast Bar in Select Units Ō×ó Deck/ Patio in Select Units Ō×ó Ensuite Bathroom in Select Units Ō×ó Fireplace in Select Units Ō×ó Granite-Style Countertops in Select Units Ō×ó Outdoor Storage in Select Units Ō×ó Pantry in Select Units Ō×ó Sunroom in Select Units Ō×ó Upgraded Fixtures in Select Units Ō×ó Wood-Style Flooring in Select Units Pets: Two pet max per apartment. - One-Time Fee: $350 for one pet $650 for two pets. - Monthly Pet Rent: $25 per pet. - Breed restrictions apply, but certified service animals (CSA) or emoti