it you at IMT Buckhead on 26th! Please copy and paste to take a video tour: https://liveimt.com/imtBuckheadYoutubeTour Price shown is Total Monthly Price including monthly mandatory fees* Monthly Mandatory Fees: - Package Locker: $5/month - Credit Reporting: $5/month - Service Fee: $6/month - Water Charges: Varies - Pest Fee: $5/month - Sewer Charges: Varies - Common Area Electricity: $10.33/month - Trash Charge: $15/month Property Amenities: ŌŚŠ Courtyard ŌŚŠ Guest Apartment ŌŚŠ Laundry Facilities ŌŚŠ Maintenance on site ŌŚŠ Package Service ŌŚŠ Pet Washing Station ŌŚŠ Picnic Area ŌŚŠ Planned Social Activities ŌŚŠ Public Transportation ŌŚŠ Tennis Court ŌŚŠ Club Room ŌŚŠ Covered Pavilion with Fireplace ŌŚŠ Dry Cleaning Concierge ŌŚŠ Easy Access to I-75, I-85 and GA 400 ŌŚŠ Elevator Building(s) ŌŚŠ Fire Pit ŌŚŠ Outdoor Grilling Stations ŌŚŠ Outdoor Pool ŌŚŠ Pool Views in Select Homes ŌŚŠ Resort-Style Clubhouse Website: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=imt_buckhead_on_26th&rp=3mjoxHPJ483t&t=wb Contact us for more information! show contact info Mon - Fri: 8:30 AM - 5:30 PM Sat: 10:00 AM - 5:00 PM Pet Ownership Policy: At IMT Buckhead on 26th, we know that the path to your heart is marked with paw prints and that the best part of your day is coming home to a wagging tail. Pets are residents, too! $300 NON-REFUNDABLE PET FEE, PER PET $25 PET RENT, PER PET. No weight restriction. Some breed restrictions apply. Please call our Leasing Center for complete Pet Policy information. Please call us for complete parking information. *Total Monthly Price includes base rent, all monthly mandatory and any user-selected optional fees. Excludes variable, usage-based, and required charges due at or prior to move-in or at move-out. Discounts, if applicable, will be calculated upon lease execution. Minimum lease terms and occupancy guidelines may apply. Deposits may vary based on credit, rental history, income, or other qualifying criteria. Additional fees and taxes may apply and will be disclosed 