        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post Monthly Price: $1788 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. SIZE: 1195 sq ft | BEDROOMS: 2 | BATHROOMS: 2 LEASE TERMS: 6-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month, 13-Month ABOUT COMMUNITY: Las Palmas Apartments Call us today! show contact info Features in this apartment home: Carpet Dishwasher Disposal/Trash Compactor Eat-in Kitchen High-Speed Internet Access Oven Patios or Balconies Range Refrigerator/Freezer Tub/Shower Custom Lighting Designer Touches Fireplaces in Select Apartment Homes Full-Size Washer Dryer Connections Hardwood Floors Premier Upgrade Unit Spacious Layouts Storage Units Total Electric Walk-In Closets About the community: Professionally managed by Ventron Management, Las Palmas Apartments offers unique apartment features unmatched in the area. Our spacious 1, 2, and 3-bedroom floorplans include full-size washer and dryer connections, fireplaces, screened-in patios, eat-in kitchens, and hardwood flooring. Upgrade options include faux hardwood flooring, granite countertops, black appliances, modern light fixtures, new cabinets, and more! Amenities at our property: Business Center Fitness Center with Cardio Screens Full-Size Washer Dryer Connections Gated Community Picnic Area Playground Smoke-Free Sparkling Pool Tennis Court Great Location Online Services Pets Allowed Preferred Employer Discounts Available Resident Social Events Screened-In Patios Serene Views Additional information: Call us today! Terms: 6-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month, 13-Month Pets: A maximum of 2 pets per unit. Pet fee: $315 (non-refundable) per pet, plus $25 monthly pet rent. Combined weight of 2 pets cannot exceed 50 lbs. Application Fee: $75 Admin Fee: $165 (both non-refundable) Prices and availability: Subject to change Website: www.apt-rental.com?n=las_palmas_apartments&rp=hqfhkb&t=wb Application: www.apt-rental.com?n=las_palmas_apartments&rp=hqfhkb&t=ap EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY Pet Policy: A maximum of 2 pet per unit shall be accepted. The pet fee is $315 Non-Refundable per pet. Monthly Pet Rent of $25. A pet addendum must be completed, and pet fees must be paid prior to moving in. If there is more than one pet per unit, the combined weight of the 2 pets cannot exceed 50lbs. CONTACT US TODAY! Las Palmas Apartments 1 Seasons Pkwy Norcross, GA 30093 Phone: show contact info Mon - Fri: 8:30 AM - 5:30 PM Sat: 10:00 AM - 5:00 PM Website: www.apt-rental.com?n=las_palmas&rp=r2MRKLkni94j&t=wb Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/LasPalmasAtlanta Professionally managed by Ventron Management Application fee is $75 and Admin Fee is $165 (both are non-refundable). All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY DD3014430A7F4E72",
