        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post East Perimeter Pointe Apartments Address: 4946 Snapfinger Woods Dr. Decatur, GA 30035 Monthly Price: $1004 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Bedrooms: 2 | Baths: 2.5 | Sq. Footage: 1018 sq ft | Terms: 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month, 13-Month Call our office at show contact info + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + Features in this apartment home: Ō×ó Air Conditioning Ō×ó Breakfast Bar Ō×ó Cable Ready Ō×ó Dining Room Ō×ó Dishwasher Ō×ó Garbage Disposal Ō×ó Island Kitchens Ō×ó Linen Closet Ō×ó Smoke Free Ō×ó Storage Units Ō×ó Fully Equipped Kitchens w/Frost-Free Refrigerator Ō×ó Hardwood Flooring Ō×ó Newly Renovated Apartments Ō×ó Patio or Balcony Options Ō×ó Roommate Floor Plans Ō×ó Townhomes Available Ō×ó Upgraded Lighting Package Ō×ó Washer & Dryer Connections + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + Amenities at our property: Ō×ó Accepts Electronic Payments Ō×ó Common Area Wi-Fi Ō×ó Community Events Ō×ó Green Community Ō×ó On-Site Maintenance Ō×ó Onsite Management Ō×ó Organized Activities Ō×ó Picnic Area Ō×ó Playground Ō×ó Swimming Pool Ō×ó Electronic Rent Payment Ō×ó Gazebo & Grilling Areas Ō×ó Monthly Resident Events Ō×ó On-site Maintenance Management Ō×ó Preferred Employer Discounts Available Ō×ó Public Transportation Ō×ó Racquetball Court(s) Ō×ó Resident Referral Bonuses Ō×ó Trail, Bike, Hike, Jog + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + About the community: Get ready for a refreshing new take on apartment living, at East Perimeter Pointe. These newly renovated apartments in Decatur, GA offer the pinnacle of comfort, convenience, and style, with spacious and streamlined 1- and 2-bedroom floor plans, top-notch amenities and a wonderful location just 20 minutes east of downtown Atlanta along I-20. Each of our dynamic and inviting apartment homes is smartly appointed with upgraded lighting packages, sunrooms, and custom paint tones, all of which work together to create a homey and inspiring environment. Our amenities list is the envy of Decatur, featuring both indoor and outdoor pools, lighted tennis courts, and a cardio and fitness center, among many other enticing attractions. Pets: A maximum of 2 pet per unit shall be accepted. The pet fee is $315 Non-Refundable per pet. A pet addendum must be completed and pet fees must be paid prior to moving in. If there is more than one pet per unit, the combined weight of the 2 pets cannot exceed 50lbs. Monthly Pet Rent of $20. For more information, please call our leasing office. Call our office at show contact info Hours: Mon - Thu: 8:30 AM - 5:30 PM Fri: 9:00 AM - 5:30 PM Sat: 10:00 AM - 5:00 PM Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/EastPerimeterPointe Website: www.lease-apts.com?n=east_perimeter_pointe&rp=rrur3ySJyZjz&t=wb Online Application: www.lease-apts.com?n=east_perimeter_pointe&rp=rrur3ySJyZjz&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.lease-apts.com?n=east_perimeter_pointe&rp=rrur3ySJyZjz&t=sch All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 5DC885803A93434E",
