        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Come home to a great community - East Perimeter Pointe Apartments! Address: 4946 Snapfinger Woods Dr. Decatur, GA 30035 Phone Number: show contact info Beds: 2 / Baths: 2 / Size: 1186 - 1307 sq ft Monthly Price: $1155 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Get ready for a refreshing new take on apartment living, at East Perimeter Pointe. These newly renovated apartments in Decatur, GA offer the pinnacle of comfort, convenience, and style, with spacious and streamlined 1- and 2-bedroom floor plans, top-notch amenities and a wonderful location just 20 minutes east of downtown Atlanta along I-20. Each of our dynamic and inviting apartment homes is smartly appointed with upgraded lighting packages, sunrooms, and custom paint tones, all of which work together to create a homey and inspiring environment. Our amenities list is the envy of Decatur, featuring both indoor and outdoor pools, lighted tennis courts, and a cardio and fitness center, among many other enticing attractions. Deposit: $400 Length of Lease: 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month, 13-Month Property Features: ŌłÆ BBQ Area ŌłÆ Business Center ŌłÆ Emergency Maintenance ŌłÆ Fax/Copy Services ŌłÆ Laundry Facilities ŌłÆ Online Leasing ŌłÆ Onsite Management ŌłÆ Outdoor Area ŌłÆ Public Transportation ŌłÆ Tennis Court(s) ŌłÆ Electronic Rent Payment ŌłÆ Gazebo & Grilling Areas ŌłÆ Monthly Resident Events ŌłÆ On-site Maintenance Management ŌłÆ Preferred Employer Discounts Available ŌłÆ Public Transportation ŌłÆ Racquetball Court(s) ŌłÆ Resident Referral Bonuses ŌłÆ Trail, Bike, Hike, Jog Apartment Amenities: ŌłÆ Air Conditioning ŌłÆ Breakfast Bar ŌłÆ Cozy Fireplaces ŌłÆ Custom Paint Tone ŌłÆ Dining Room ŌłÆ Dishwasher ŌłÆ Garbage Disposal ŌłÆ Linen Closet ŌłÆ Smoke Free ŌłÆ Sunrooms ŌłÆ Fully Equipped Kitchens w/Frost-Free Refrigerator ŌłÆ Hardwood Flooring ŌłÆ Newly Renovated Apartments ŌłÆ Patio or Balcony Options ŌłÆ Roommate Floor Plans ŌłÆ Townhomes Available ŌłÆ Upgraded Lighting Package ŌłÆ Washer & Dryer Connections Pets: A maximum of 2 pet per unit shall be accepted. The pet fee is $315 Non-Refundable per pet. A pet addendum must be completed and pet fees must be paid prior to moving in. If there is more than one pet per unit, the combined weight of the 2 pets cannot exceed 50lbs. Monthly Pet Rent of $20. For more information, please call our leasing office. Business Hours: Mon - Thu: 8:30 AM - 5:30 PM Fri: 9:00 AM - 5:30 PM Sat: 10:00 AM - 5:00 PM Ready to Lease? Phone Number: show contact info Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/EastPerimeterPointe Website: www.rentalsapts.com?n=east_perimeter_pointe&rp=hVRH1QXRhYBb&t=wb Online Application: www.rentalsapts.com?n=east_perimeter_pointe&rp=hVRH1QXRhYBb&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.rentalsapts.com?n=east_perimeter_pointe&rp=hVRH1QXRhYBb&t=sch All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 2DC5458DD3F2464D",
