        "geocode_query": "4946 Snapfinger Woods Dr.",
        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post East Perimeter Pointe Apartments Address: 4946 Snapfinger Woods Dr. Decatur, GA 30035 Monthly Price: $888 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Bedrooms: 1 | Baths: 1 | Sq. Footage: 555 sq ft | Terms: 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month, 13-Month Call us today at show contact info + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + Features in this apartment home: ŌØ¢ Air Conditioning ŌØ¢ Breakfast Bar ŌØ¢ Cozy Fireplaces ŌØ¢ Custom Paint Tone ŌØ¢ Dining Room ŌØ¢ Dishwasher ŌØ¢ Garbage Disposal ŌØ¢ Island Kitchens ŌØ¢ Linen Closet ŌØ¢ Storage Units ŌØ¢ Fully Equipped Kitchens w/Frost-Free Refrigerator ŌØ¢ Hardwood Flooring ŌØ¢ Newly Renovated Apartments ŌØ¢ Patio or Balcony Options ŌØ¢ Roommate Floor Plans ŌØ¢ Townhomes Available ŌØ¢ Upgraded Lighting Package + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + Amenities at our property: ŌØ¢ 24 Hour Availability ŌØ¢ Accepts Electronic Payments ŌØ¢ Fax/Copy Services ŌØ¢ Fitness Center ŌØ¢ Indoor Pool ŌØ¢ Onsite Management ŌØ¢ Organized Activities ŌØ¢ Pet Friendly ŌØ¢ Playground ŌØ¢ Valet Trash ŌØ¢ Electronic Rent Payment ŌØ¢ Gazebo & Grilling Areas ŌØ¢ Monthly Resident Events ŌØ¢ On-site Maintenance Management ŌØ¢ Preferred Employer Discounts Available ŌØ¢ Public Transportation ŌØ¢ Racquetball Court(s) ŌØ¢ Resident Referral Bonuses ŌØ¢ Trail, Bike, Hike, Jog + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + About the community: Get ready for a refreshing new take on apartment living, at East Perimeter Pointe. These newly renovated apartments in Decatur, GA offer the pinnacle of comfort, convenience, and style, with spacious and streamlined 1- and 2-bedroom floor plans, top-notch amenities and a wonderful location just 20 minutes east of downtown Atlanta along I-20. Each of our dynamic and inviting apartment homes is smartly appointed with upgraded lighting packages, sunrooms, and custom paint tones, all of which work together to create a homey and inspiring environment. Our amenities list is the envy of Decatur, featuring both indoor and outdoor pools, lighted tennis courts, and a cardio and fitness center, among many other enticing attractions. Pets: A maximum of 2 pet per unit shall be accepted. The pet fee is $315 Non-Refundable per pet. A pet addendum must be completed and pet fees must be paid prior to moving in. If there is more than one pet per unit, the combined weight of the 2 pets cannot exceed 50lbs. Monthly Pet Rent of $20. For more information, please call our leasing office. Call us today at show contact info Hours: Mon - Thu: 8:30 AM - 5:30 PM Fri: 9:00 AM - 5:30 PM Sat: 10:00 AM - 5:00 PM Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/EastPerimeterPointe Website: www.apts-rental.com?n=east_perimeter_pointe&rp=tPCQtmi619RH&t=wb Online Application: www.apts-rental.com?n=east_perimeter_pointe&rp=tPCQtmi619RH&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.apts-rental.com?n=east_perimeter_pointe&rp=tPCQtmi619RH&t=sch All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 2640529D7B6F4567",
