om?n=embarcadero_club&rp=xhzis3&t=ap Additional Information Application Fee: $75 (Non-Refundable) Admin Fee: $165 (Non-Refundable) Prices and availability are subject to change. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY His and her closets and spacious living and dining area Rental Information: 2 Bedroom / 1 Bathroom / 865 sq ft Monthly Price: $1119 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Lease Terms: 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month Leasing Hours: Mon - Fri: 8:30 AM - 5:30 PM Sat: 10:00 AM - 5:00 PM Pet Policy: A maximum of 2 pet per unit shall be accepted. The pet fee is $315 Non-Refundable per pet. Pet Monthly rent of $25. A pet addendum must be completed, and pet fees must be paid prior to moving in. If there is more than one pet per unit, the combined weight of the 2 pets cannot exceed 50lbs. No aggressive breeds. Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/EmbarcaderoClubApartments Website: www.apts-rental.com?n=embarcadero_club&rp=hwtu6DdqrS3w&t=wb Management Company: Ventron Management All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 83FFECFDD95B4D",
