        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post Come home to a great community - Embarcadero Club! Address: 2210 Sullivan Road College Park, GA 30337 Beds: 1 / Baths: 1 / Size: 700 sq ft Monthly Price: $824 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Embarcadero Club Apartments Call us for more information! show contact info Description Embarcadero Club Apartments is in a fabulous location. Not only are we directly on the MARTA bus line, but we are only minutes from Hartsfield-Jackson Airport, Clayton State University, Southern Regional Medical, Turner Field, and numerous restaurants and retail establishments. We are also just a few miles from major interstates and a short commute to Downtown Atlanta and Henry County. This home has 3 hallway closets. TONS of storage! Lease Terms 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month Pet Policy A maximum of 2 pets per unit is accepted. The pet fee is $315 (Non-Refundable) per pet. Monthly pet rent is $25. A pet addendum must be completed, and pet fees must be paid prior to moving in. If there is more than one pet per unit, the combined weight of the two pets cannot exceed 50 lbs. No aggressive breeds. Apartment Amenities Air Conditioning Balcony Carpet Ceiling Fans Deck Dishwasher Disposal Window Coverings Cable Ready High-Speed Internet Access Microwave Views Walk-In Closets Washer/Dryer Hookup Wheelchair Accessible (Rooms) Community Features BBQ/Picnic Area Business Center Courtyard Fitness Center Laundry Facilities Maintenance On-Site Parking Picnic Area Playground Sparkling Pool Convenient to I-285 Courtesy Patrol Less Than 5 Minutes To Hartsfield-Jackson Lighted Tennis Courts Mature Landscaping Package Service Pet Care Property Manager On-Site Public Transportation Relaxing Saunas Location & Contact Address: 2210 Sullivan Road, College Park, GA 30337 Call us for more information: show contact info Hours Mon - Fri: 8:30 AM - 5:30 PM Sat: 10:00 A