        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Ashland Pines Located at: 1247 Adcox Road Stone Mountain, GA 30088 Featured apartment home: 1 bed | 1 bath | 704 sq ft Monthly Price: $1036 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Call: show contact info Ashland Pines is a luxury apartment community in Stone Mountain with an array of custom features and amenities designed to ease your busy lifestyle. Conveniently located on Hairston Road, your new home is within minutes of I-285, Stone Mountain Park, Dekalb Medical Center and the Mall at Stonecrest. The expansive 1 and 2 bedroom floor plans and amenities provide an opportunity for you to comfortably relax at home, grill up some food by our over-sized pool or undertake a vigorous workout in our fitness center. Wonderful Amenities! ŌŚŠ BBQ/Picnic Area ŌŚŠ Conference Room ŌŚŠ Courtyard ŌŚŠ Fitness Center ŌŚŠ Grill ŌŚŠ Maintenance/Manager on site ŌŚŠ Public Transportation ŌŚŠ Security System ŌŚŠ Smoke Free ŌŚŠ Cable/Satellite Available ŌŚŠ Dog Park Pet Care ŌŚŠ Online Services ŌŚŠ Planned Community Activities ŌŚŠ Sports Courts ŌŚŠ Sundeck ŌŚŠ Walking Distance to Shopping and Dining ŌŚŠ Wi-Fi at Pool and Clubhouse ŌŚŠ Wireless Internet Available Apartment Features! ŌŚŠ Balcony/Patio ŌŚŠ Cable Ready ŌŚŠ Carpeting ŌŚŠ Ceiling Fans ŌŚŠ Dishwasher ŌŚŠ Kitchen ŌŚŠ Storage Units ŌŚŠ Stove ŌŚŠ Tub/Shower ŌŚŠ Views ŌŚŠ Dining Room ŌŚŠ Hardwood Floors ŌŚŠ Linen Closet ŌŚŠ Refrigerator/Freezer ŌŚŠ Trash Compactor ŌŚŠ Walk-In Closets ŌŚŠ Washer/Dryer Hookup ŌŚŠ Wood Burning Fireplace Hours: Mon - Fri: 8:30 AM - 5:30 PM Sat: 10:00 AM - 5:00 PM Sun: 1:00 PM - 5:00 PM Call: show contact info Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/ashlandpinesapts/ Website: www.apt-rental.com?n=ashland_pines&rp=mRkH6bM45T7F&t=wb Online Application: www.apt-rental.com?n=ashland_pines&rp=mRkH6bM45T7F&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.apt-rental.com?n=ashland_pines&rp=mRkH6bM45T7F&t=sch Terms: 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month Pet Policy: A maximum of 2 pet per unit shall be accepted. The pet fee is $325 Non-Refundable per pet. A pet addendum must be completed and pet fees must be paid prior to moving in. If there is more than one pet per unit, the combined weight of the 2 pets cannot exceed 50lbs.Monthly pet rent: $25 per pet All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 2E55A3A7930349",
