        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Spring Lake Apartments - A place to call home! Bed: 2 / Bath: 2 Sq. Footage: 1158 sq ft Monthly Price: $1219 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Terms: 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month Office Phone: show contact info Spring Lake Apartments is in a fabulous location. Not only are we within minutes from Clayton State University, but we are also minutes from Southlake Mall, Piedmont Henry Hospital, Gillem Logistics Center, and numerous shops and restaurants. We are only a few miles from major interstates and a short commute to Downtown Atlanta. Our Apartment Homes Feature: ŌŚŠ Balcony/Patio ŌŚŠ Dishwasher ŌŚŠ Disposal ŌŚŠ Lake views ŌŚŠ Linen Closets ŌŚŠ Oven/Range ŌŚŠ Spacious Sunrooms ŌŚŠ Storage Units ŌŚŠ W/D Connections ŌŚŠ Walk-In Closets ŌŚŠ Air Conditioning and Heating ŌŚŠ Brushed Nickel Lighting ŌŚŠ Ceiling Fans with Lighting ŌŚŠ Classic Two-Tone Paint ŌŚŠ Fully Equipped Kitchens ŌŚŠ Granite Inspired Countertops ŌŚŠ High Speed Internet Access ŌŚŠ Refrigerator and Freezer/Ice Maker ŌŚŠ Renovated Suites Available ŌŚŠ Separate Dining Areas Our Residents Enjoy: ŌŚŠ Clothes Care Center ŌŚŠ Clubhouse w/WIFI ŌŚŠ Clubroom ŌŚŠ Courtyard ŌŚŠ Fitness Center ŌŚŠ Package Receiving ŌŚŠ Pet Care ŌŚŠ Waterfront ŌŚŠ Community Playground ŌŚŠ Flexible Lease Terms ŌŚŠ Maintenance on site ŌŚŠ Picnic Areas & Gazebos ŌŚŠ Picnic Pavilion with Grills ŌŚŠ Relaxing Community Lake ŌŚŠ Relaxing Community Lake & Pavilion ŌŚŠ Resort Inspired Pool Office Phone: show contact info 7000 Southlake Pkwy Morrow, GA 30260 Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/springlakeatl Website: www.rentalsapts.com?n=spring_lake&rp=r7W1N3J17KNg&t=wb Online Application: www.rentalsapts.com?n=spring_lake&rp=r7W1N3J17KNg&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.rentalsapts.com?n=spring_lake&rp=r7W1N3J17KNg&t=sch Mon - Fri: 8:30 AM - 5:30 PM Sat: 10:00 AM - 5:00 PM Pets: Spring Lake Apartments is a pet-friendly community that welcomes two pets per apartment home. The pet fee is $300 non-refundable per pet. Monthly Pet Rent is $25. A pet addendum must be completed, and pet fees must be paid prior to moving in. If there is more than one pet per unit, the combined weight of the 2 pets cannot exceed 50 lbs. Breed restrictions may apply. All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 8367192B970C4C4",
