        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Brighton Way Located at: 100 Parkway Avenue Smyrna, GA 30080 Featured apartment home: 1 bed | 1 bath | 842 sq ft Monthly Price: $1070 - $1460 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Reach out via phone: show contact info Brighton Way is ideal for anyone seeking a quiet, well-connected place to live near Atlanta. Our pet-friendly community combines suburban charm with modern convenience, offering a lifestyle that's both relaxed and accessible. Wonderful Amenities! ŌŚŠ Ample Parking ŌŚŠ Availability 24 Hours ŌŚŠ Courtesy Officer ŌŚŠ On-Site Maintenance ŌŚŠ On-Site Management ŌŚŠ Outdoor Grilling Areas ŌŚŠ Package Receiving ŌŚŠ Picnic Area by the Pool ŌŚŠ Sparkling Pool with Sun Soaked Seating ŌŚŠ Swimming Pool and Sundeck Apartment Features! ŌŚŠ Air Conditioner ŌŚŠ Cable/satellite ŌŚŠ Ceiling Fan in select units ŌŚŠ Dishwasher ŌŚŠ Disposal ŌŚŠ Fireplace* ŌŚŠ Fully Equipped Kitchens ŌŚŠ Garbage Disposal ŌŚŠ Refrigerator ŌŚŠ W/D Hookup ŌŚŠ High Vaulted Ceilings in third floor units ŌŚŠ Large Walk-in Closets ŌŚŠ Private Balcony- Patio Hours: Mon - Fri: 9:00 AM - 5:00 PM Reach out via phone: show contact info Website: www.apt-rental.com?n=brighton_way&rp=axiwfwnE9UkR&t=wb Online Application: www.apt-rental.com?n=brighton_way&rp=axiwfwnE9UkR&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.apt-rental.com?n=brighton_way&rp=axiwfwnE9UkR&t=sch Terms: 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month, 13-Month, 14-Month, 15-Month Pet Policy: Pet Guidelines Allowed pets include dogs, cats, fish, birds, and hamsters Pet fees or pet rent apply to dogs and cats only Up to two pets per home Exotic pets or livestock are not permitted Fish tanks may not exceed 24 gallons Breed Restrictions For more information on restrictions or pet-related fees, contact our leasing team. We're happy to help you and your pets find the purr-fect fit! Administrative Fee $110 All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 3NS0N2ITTSI1M80",
