ment home. The pet fee is $325 non-refundable per pet. There is a $20 monthly pet rent. A pet addendum must be completed, and pet fees must be paid prior to moving in. If there is more than one pet per unit, the combined weight of the 2 pets cannot exceed 50 lbs. Breed restrictions may apply. Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/brooksideparkatlanta Website: www.apt-rental.com?n=brookside_park&rp=ag1xYnShN17a&t=wb Online Application: www.apt-rental.com?n=brookside_park&rp=ag1xYnShN17a&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.apt-rental.com?n=brookside_park&rp=ag1xYnShN17a&t=sch All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY A943E06E4E074D",
