        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post IMT Buckhead on 26th Featured Floorplan: 2-bed / 2-bath / 1061 sq ft Monthly Price: $1815 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Deposit: Call Call us at show contact info Description: IMT Buckhead on 26th also offers a world-class 24-hour fitness facility, with 4 Peloton Bikes and Fitness on Demand workout programs. The available apartment homes offer a wide variety of luxury living options, including studios, one-bedrooms, two-bedroom, and townhome-style three bedrooms! Please copy and paste to take a video tour: https://liveimt.com/imtBuckheadYoutubeTour Price shown is Total Monthly Price including monthly mandatory fees* Monthly Mandatory Fees: - Package Locker: $5/month - Credit Reporting: $5/month - Service Fee: $6/month - Water Charges: Varies - Pest Fee: $5/month - Sewer Charges: Varies - Common Area Electricity: $10.33/month - Trash Charge: $15/month Lease Terms: 3-Month, 4-Month, 5-Month, 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month Pet Policy: At IMT Buckhead on 26th, we know that the path to your heart is marked with paw prints and that the best part of your day is coming home to a wagging tail. Pets are residents, too! $300 NON-REFUNDABLE PET FEE, PER PET $25 PET RENT, PER PET. No weight restriction. Some breed restrictions apply. Please call our Leasing Center for complete Pet Policy information. Apartment Amenities: ŌłÆ Air Conditioning ŌłÆ Cable Ready ŌłÆ Ceiling Fans ŌłÆ Crown Molding ŌłÆ Deck ŌłÆ Dining Room ŌłÆ Dishwasher ŌłÆ Disposal ŌłÆ Double Vanities ŌłÆ Eat-in Kitchen ŌłÆ High Speed Internet Access ŌłÆ Instant Hot Water ŌłÆ Island Kitchen ŌłÆ Linen Closet ŌłÆ Microwave ŌłÆ Oven/Range ŌłÆ Pantry ŌłÆ Refrigerator/Freezer/Ice Maker ŌłÆ Storage Units ŌłÆ Trash Compactor ŌłÆ Tub/Shower ŌłÆ Vaulted Ceiling ŌłÆ Views ŌłÆ Walk-In Closets ŌłÆ Wheelchair Accessible (Rooms) ŌłÆ Window Coverings ŌłÆ Black Appliances in Classic Home ŌłÆ Double-Basin Sink with Pull-Down Sprayer in Upgraded Homes ŌłÆ Fireplaces in Select Homes ŌłÆ Granite Countertops in Classic Homes ŌłÆ Hard Surface Countertops ŌłÆ Individual Climate Control ŌłÆ Plush Carpeting in Living Areas ŌłÆ Skyline Views in Select Homes ŌłÆ Stainless Steel Appliances in Upgraded Homes ŌłÆ Tile Flooring in Classic Homes ŌłÆ USB Port in Kitchen in Upgraded Homes ŌłÆ Washers and Dryers in Select Homes ŌłÆ White Ceiling Fans in Classic Homes Community Features: ŌłÆ Bike Storage ŌłÆ Controlled Access ŌłÆ Lounge ŌłÆ Maintenance on site ŌłÆ Package Service ŌłÆ Pet Washing Station ŌłÆ Property Manager on Site ŌłÆ Recycling ŌłÆ Storage Space ŌłÆ Walking/Biking Trails ŌłÆ Business / Conference Center ŌłÆ Club Room ŌłÆ Easy Access to I-75, I-85 and GA 400 ŌłÆ Elevator Building(s) ŌłÆ Fire Pit ŌłÆ Outdoor Grilling Stations ŌłÆ Outdoor Pool ŌłÆ Pool Views in Select Homes ŌłÆ Professionally Managed ŌłÆ Resort-Style Clubhouse Address: 225 26th St NW Atlanta, GA 30309 Call us at show contact info Mon - Fri: 8:30 AM - 5:30 PM Sat: 10:00 AM - 5:00 PM Website: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=imt_buckhead_on_26th&rp=8FpWD8V7Mxai&t=wb Please call us for complete parking information. *Total Monthly Price includes base rent, all monthly mandatory and any user-selected optional fees. Excludes variable, usage-based, and required charges due at or prior to move-in or at move-out. Discounts, if applicable, will be calculated upon lease execution. Minimum lease terms and occupancy guidelines may apply. Deposits may vary based on credit, rental history, income, or other qualifying criteria. Additional fees and taxes may apply and will be disclosed per governing laws and company policies. Total Monthly Price may be displayed as a whole dollar amount for advertising purposes only; actual charges are calculated using exact fee amounts, including cents, and may vary from the displayed amount by up to 50 cents due to rounding. Price shown is Total Monthly Price including monthly mandatory fees* Monthly Mandatory Fees: - Package Locker: $5/month - Credit Reporting: $5/month - Service Fee: $6/month - Water Charges: Varies - Pest Fee: $5/month - Sewer Charges: Varies - Common Area Electricity: $10.33/month - Trash Charge: $15/month All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 7921DF4CFA40493",
