        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post RENTAL INFO Monthly Price: $1640 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. IMT Alpharetta: 3500 North Point Parkway Alpharetta, GA 30005 Apartment for Rent: 1-BR 1-BA | Square Feet: 725 sq ft | Lease Length: 3-Month, 4-Month, 5-Month, 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month Phone: show contact info PROPERTY AMENITIES ŌŚÅ Car Care Center ŌŚÅ Playground ŌŚÅ Pool ŌŚÅ Access to Big Creek Greenway Walking Trails ŌŚÅ Close Proximity to Avalon Shopping District & North Point Mall ŌŚÅ Emergency Maintenance Service ŌŚÅ Lighted Tennis Court ŌŚÅ MARTA Public Transportation Access ŌŚÅ Online & On-Site Kiosk Access ŌŚÅ Resort-Style Pool with Lap Lanes ŌŚÅ Within Blue Award Winning Webb Bridge Middle & Alpharetta High School Districts APARTMENT AMENITIES ŌŚÅ Black or Stainless Steel Appliances in Classic Hom ŌŚÅ Ceiling Fan ŌŚÅ Custom Oak Cabinetry ŌŚÅ Detached Garages in Select Homes ŌŚÅ Eight-Foot Ceilings ŌŚÅ Granite Countertops in Upgraded Homes ŌŚÅ Lighted Ceiling Fans ŌŚÅ Private Balcony/Patio in Select Homes ŌŚÅ Walk-In Closets ŌŚÅ Wood-Style Flooring in Living Areas in Upgraded Homes ADDITIONAL INFO Description: **Walk-ins welcome & choose from 3 tour options.** IMT Alpharetta is comprised of one-, two- and three-bedroom apartment homes located in the beautiful suburb of Alpharetta, GA. Each home includes an array of interior amenities from fully equipped gourmet kitchens to in-home washer/dryers to a private patio, balcony or sunroom, perfect for relaxation. Community amenities include two lighted tennis courts, a resort-style pool, a playground and more. Lease terms are 3-12, 24. Take a Virtual Tour of Our Property Today! https://liveimt.com/imtAlpharettaYoutubeTour Price shown is Total Monthly Price including monthly mandatory fees* Monthly Mandatory Fees: - Package Locker: $5/month - Credit Reporting: $5/month - Water Charges: Varies - Sewer Charges: Varies - Pest: $4.50/month - Service Fee: $3.99/month - Trash Service: $10/month Pet Policy: Pets allowed! Two pet maximum. Pet fee (non-refundable) is $300 per pet. Pet rent is $25 per month per pet. No weight restrictions. Some breed restrictions apply. Website: www.rentalsapts.com?n=imt_alpharetta&rp=kdRjqfhgxF6C&t=wb Phone: show contact info *Total Monthly Price includes base rent, all monthly mandatory and any user-selected optional fees. Excludes variable, usage-based, and required charges due at or prior to move-in or at move-out. Discounts, if applicable, will be calculated upon lease execution. Minimum lease terms and occupancy guidelines may apply. Deposits may vary based on credit, rental history, income, or other qualifying criteria. Additional fees and taxes may apply and will be disclosed per governing laws and company policies. Total Monthly Price may be displayed as a whole dollar amount for advertising purposes only; actual charges are calculated using exact fee amounts, including cents, and may vary from the displayed amount by up to 50 cents due to rounding. Price shown is Total Monthly Price including monthly mandatory fees* Monthly Mandatory Fees: - Package Locker: $5/month - Credit Reporting: $5/month - Water Charges: Varies - Sewer Charges: Varies - Pest: $4.50/month - Service Fee: $3.99/month - Trash Service: $10/month All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY A4E8FEFC43694D1",
