        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post RENTAL INFO Monthly Price: $1640 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. IMT Alpharetta: 3500 North Point Parkway Alpharetta, GA 30005 Apartment for Rent: 1-BR 1-BA | Square Feet: 725 sq ft | Lease Length: 3-Month, 4-Month, 5-Month, 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month Phone: show contact info PROPERTY AMENITIES ŌŚÅ Car Care Center ŌŚÅ Playground ŌŚÅ Pool ŌŚÅ Access to Big Creek Greenway Walking Trails ŌŚÅ Close Proximity to Avalon Shopping District & North Point Mall ŌŚÅ Emergency Maintenance Service ŌŚÅ Lighted Tennis Court ŌŚÅ MARTA Public Transportation Access ŌŚÅ Online & On-Site Kiosk Access ŌŚÅ Resort-Style Pool with Lap Lanes ŌŚÅ Within Blue Award Winning Webb Bridge Middle & Alpharetta High School Districts APARTMENT AMENITIES ŌŚÅ Black or Stainless Steel Appliances in Classic Hom ŌŚÅ Ceiling Fan ŌŚÅ Custom Oak Cabinetry ŌŚÅ Detached Garages in Select Homes ŌŚÅ Eight-Foot Ceilings ŌŚÅ Granite Countertops in Upgraded Homes ŌŚÅ Lighted Ceiling Fans ŌŚÅ Private Balcony/Patio in Select Homes ŌŚÅ Walk-In Closets ŌŚÅ Wood-Style Flooring in Living Areas in Upgraded Homes ADDITIONAL INFO Description: **Walk-ins welcome & choose from 3 tour options.** IMT Alpharetta is comprised of one-, two- and three-bedroom apartment homes located in the beautiful suburb of Alpharetta, GA. Each home includes an array of interior amenities from fully equipped gourmet kitchens to in-home washer/dryers to a private patio, balcony or sunroom, perfect for relaxation. Community amenities include two lighted tennis courts, a resort-style pool, a playground and more. Lease terms are 3-12, 24. Take a Virtual Tour of Our Property Today! https://liveimt.com/imtAlpharettaYoutubeTour Price shown is Total Monthly Price including monthly mandatory fees* Monthly Mandatory Fees: - Package Locker: $5/month - Credit Reporting: $5/month - Water Charges: Varies - 