        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post East Perimeter Pointe Apartments Address: 4946 Snapfinger Woods Dr. Decatur, GA 30035 Monthly Price: $973 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Bedrooms: 1 | Baths: 1 | Sq. Footage: 770 - 889 sq ft | Terms: 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month, 13-Month Call us: show contact info $200 off your 1st month's rent + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + Features in this apartment home: ŌłÆ Air Conditioning ŌłÆ Cable Ready ŌłÆ Dining Room ŌłÆ Dishwasher ŌłÆ Garbage Disposal ŌłÆ Island Kitchens ŌłÆ Linen Closet ŌłÆ Smoke Free ŌłÆ Storage Units ŌłÆ Sunrooms ŌłÆ Fully Equipped Kitchens w/Frost-Free Refrigerator ŌłÆ Hardwood Flooring ŌłÆ Newly Renovated Apartments ŌłÆ Patio or Balcony Options ŌłÆ Roommate Floor Plans ŌłÆ Townhomes Available ŌłÆ Upgraded Lighting Package ŌłÆ Washer & Dryer Connections + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + Amenities at our property: ŌłÆ BBQ Area ŌłÆ Community Events ŌłÆ Indoor Pool ŌłÆ Online Leasing ŌłÆ On-Site Maintenance ŌłÆ Outdoor Area ŌłÆ Pet Friendly ŌłÆ Storage Space ŌłÆ Tennis Court(s) ŌłÆ Valet Trash ŌłÆ Electronic Rent Payment ŌłÆ Gazebo & Grilling Areas ŌłÆ Monthly Resident Events ŌłÆ On-site Maintenance Management ŌłÆ Preferred Employer Discounts Available ŌłÆ Public Transportation ŌłÆ Racquetball Court(s) ŌłÆ Resident Referral Bonuses ŌłÆ Trail, Bike, Hike, Jog + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + About the community: The thriving neighborhood of East Decatur is uniquely suited to your apartment needs, offering peace and tranquility while keeping you engaged with the culture and excitement of the greater Atlanta area. You can enjoy a mere 15-minute drive to downtown Decatur and a short 20-minute drive to the airport. You'll also have easy access to nearby Atlanta Transit for your commuting needs. There's simply no reason not to make these singular Decatur, GA Apartments your new home. Pets: A maximum of 2 pet per unit shall be accepted. The pet fee is $315 Non-Refundable per pet. A pet addendum must be completed and pet fees must be paid prior to moving in. If there is more than one pet per unit, the combined weight of the 2 pets cannot exceed 50lbs. Monthly Pet Rent of $20. For more information, please call our leasing office. Call us: show contact info Hours: Mon - Thu: 8:30 AM - 5:30 PM Fri: 9:00 AM - 5:30 PM Sat: 10:00 AM - 5:00 PM Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/EastPerimeterPointe Website: www.lease-apts.com?n=east_perimeter_pointe&rp=uBupTbPVDvKX&t=wb Online Application: www.lease-apts.com?n=east_perimeter_pointe&rp=uBupTbPVDvKX&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.lease-apts.com?n=east_perimeter_pointe&rp=uBupTbPVDvKX&t=sch All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY C12E7C9B78AD474E",
